hadiths[303]{hadithnumber,text}:
3079,Hazrat Imam Behaqi ne usey Shobil-emaan mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki sanad se riwayat kiya hai. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan).
3080,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nojawanon ki jamaat ! tum mein se jo shakhs jima aur nikah ke ikhrajat ki istataat rakhta ho to wo shaadi karey, kyonkey wo nigahon ko neecha rakhney aur iffat aur ismat ki hifazat ke liye ziyada muassar (asardar) hai, aur jo shakhs (aqd nikah ki) istataat (taqat) na rakhey to wo roza rakhey, kyonkey ye uski shehwat kam karney ka baais hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3081,"Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Usman bin Mazoon (Raziallahu anhu) ki tarak nikah (na karne) ki soch ko radd farmaya , aur agar aap unhen ijazat dey detey to ham khassi ho jatey. muttafaq aleh."
3082,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aurat se chaar chizon, uskey maal , uskey hasab aur nasab , uskey Husn aur jamaal aur uskey Deen ki wajeh se nikah kiya jata hai, terey haath khaak aalud hon tum Deen daar ke sath nikah karkey kamiyabi hasil karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
3083,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''duniya mukammal taur par mataa (daulat) hai, aur behtareen mataae (daulate) duniya nek biwi hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3084,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''oonton par Sawar honey wali (arab) aurton mein sey, Quraish ki nek khawatin behtar hain. wo apney chhotey bachon par nihayat shafiq aur shohar ke maal ki intehai muhafiz hoti hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
3085,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main apney baad mardon ke liye aurton se ziyada nuksandeh koi fitna khayal nahin karta.'' muttafaq aleh."
3086,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''duniya sheereen (meethi) aur sarsabz aur shadab hai, be-shak Allah Taala tumhen is mein khalifa bananey wala hai, wo dekhega ke tum kaisey amaal kartey ho, tum duniya aur aurton ke fitney se bacho , kyonkey Bani-Israel ka pehla fitna aurton ki wajeh se roonumaa hua (saamne aaya).'' rawahu Muslim."
3087,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aurat , ghar aur ghodey mein nahusat (yani be barkati) hai.'' Bukhari, Muslim. aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''teen chizon mein nahusat hai aurat, ghar aur janwer.'' muttafaq aleh."
3088,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath eik ghazwe mein shareek they, jab ham wapis aaye aur Madina ke qarib pahunchey to maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! maine naee naee shaadi ki hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne shaadi kar li?'' maine arz kiya : ji haan ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kanwari se ya bewa se?'' maine arz kiya : ji ! bewa sey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne kanwari se shaadi kyon na ki, tum us se kheltey aur wo tum se khelti.'' jab ham (Madina ke) qarib pahunch gaey aur is mein dakhil honey lagey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''thehar jaao yahan tak ke ham raat yani Isha ke waqt dakhil hongey taake muntashir baalon wali kanghi kar ley aur jis ka khawind (shohar) ghayeb raha ho wo zere naaf baal saaf kar ley.'' muttafaq aleh."
3089,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen qism ke logon, wo ghulam jisne azaadi paane ke liye muhaida kiya ho, jo ke adaegi chahta ho, iffat aur paak damani ki khatir nikah karney waley aur Allah ki raah mein jihad karney waley ki Allah zarur madad karta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Nasai aur ibne-Maja."
3090,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tumharey paas kisi aisey shakhs ka peghame-nikah aaye jis ka Deen aur akhlaq aur aadaat tumhen pasand hon to usey bachchi ka rishta deydo, agar aisa na karogey to phir zamin mein fitna aur bada fasad hoga.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3091,"Hazrat Maaqil bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shohar se ziyada mohabbat karney wali aur ziyada bachon ko janm deney wali aurton se shaadi karo, kyonkey main tumhari kasrat ki wajeh se deegar ummaton par fakhr karunga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3092,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Salim bin Utba bin Aweem bin Saaida Ansari apney walid (Saalim) se wo uskey dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum kanwari ladkiyon se shaadi karo, kyonkey wo sheereen guftaar (meetha bolne wali), ziyada bachchon ko janne wali aur bahut kam chiz par razi ho janey wali hain.'' ibne-Maja , riwayat mursal hai. rawahu ibne-Maja."
3093,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne nikah (yani khawind aur biwi ( ki jaisi do baham (aapas mein) mohabbat karney waley nahin dekhey hongey.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
3094,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs pakizah haalat mein Allah se mulaqat karney ka khahish mand ho to usey azad aurton se shaadi karni chahiye.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
3095,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin ne Allah ke taqwe ke baad apney liye jis khair se istifaada kiya, wo nek biwi hai, agar us (momin) ne usey hukm diya to us (biwi) ne uski itaat ki, agar usney uski taraf dekha to usney usey khush kar diya, agar usney usey qism de-di to usney usey pura kiya aur agar wo uskey paas se chala gaya to usney apni jaan aur uskey maal mein us se khair-khahi ki.'' teeno ahadis ibne-Maja ne riwayat ki hain. rawahu ibne-Maja."
3096,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab banda shaadi kar leta hai to wo nisf (aadha) Deen mukammal kar leta hai, usey baqi aadhe mein Allah se darna chahiye.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
3097,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo nikah sab se ziyada ba-barkat hai, jis mein ikhrajat kam hon.'' Imam Behaqi (Raziallahu anhu) ne dono ahadis ko Shobil-emaan mein riwayat kiya hai. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
3098,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kiya : maine ansaar ki eik aurat se shaadi karney ka irada kiya hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey dekh lo , kyonkey ansaar ki aakhon mein kuchh (nuqs) hota hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3099,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aurat, aurat ke sath jism na milaaey, phir wo iskey mutalliq apney khawind se bayan karey goya ke wo usey dekh raha hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3100,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aadmi, aadmi ki sharm-gah ki taraf dekhey na aurat, aurat ki sharm-gah ki taraf dekhey aur na hi mard, mard ke sath eik kapdey mein letey aur na hi aurat, aurat ke sath eik kapdey mein letey.'' rawahu Muslim."
3101,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sun lo ! koi aadmi kisi bewa aurat ke yahan raat basar na karey magar ye ke wo (us ka ( shohar ho ya Mohrim ho.'' rawahu Muslim."
3102,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aurton ke paas janey se bacho.'' kisi aadmi ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! daiwar ke barey mein bataeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''daiwar to maut hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3103,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne pachhney lagwaaney ke mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ijazat talab ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abu-Taiba ko hukm farmaya ke wo unhen pachhney lagaey, raawi bayan kartey hain, mera khayal hai ke wo (Abu-Taiba) Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke razaai bhai they ya nabaligh ladkey they. rawahu Muslim."
3104,"Hazrat Jarir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine achcha uth janey wali nazar ke mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey hukm farmaya ke main apni nazar hata lun. rawahu Muslim."
3105,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak aurat shetan ki surat mein samney aati hai aur shetan ki surat mein mud'ti hai, jab koi aurat tum mein se kisi ko bhali lagey aur wo uskey dil mein ghar kar jaey to wo aadmi apni biwi ke paas aaye aur us se jima karey, kyonkey ye chiz (jimaa) us (gunah ke khayal) ko door kar deygi jo uskey dil mein hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3106,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi aurat ko peghame-nikah bhejey to phir agar wo us se daaiya nikah (aurat ki shakal aur surat waghera) ko dekh sakey to dekh ley.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3107,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine eik aurat ko peghame-nikah bheja to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''kya tum ne usey dekha hai? ''maine arz kiya : nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey dekh lo, kyonkey wo ziyada munasib hai ke tum dono ke darmiyan mohabbat dal di jaey.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi, Nasai, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
3108,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kisi aurat ko dekha to wo aap ko achchi lagi , aap Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ke paas tashrif laye, wo us waqt khushbu tayyar kar rahi thin aur unke paas kuchch aurten thin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen alehda kiya aur apni hajat puri ki phir farmaya : ''koi aadmi kisi aurat ko dekhey aur wo usey khush lagey to wo aadmi apni ehliya ke paas aaye kyonkey uskey paas bhi wohi kuch hai jo us aurat ke paas hai.'' rawahu Darmi."
3109,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aurat parda hai, jab wo (be parda) nikalti hai to shetan usey muzayyan (saji hui) karkey dikhata hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3110,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''Ali ! (kisi ajnabi aurat ko) lagataar na dekh, kyonkey tum (ghair iraadi taur par) pehli baar dekh saktey ho jabkey dusri martaba dekhney ka tumhen haq hasil nahin.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
3111,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi apney ghulam ki shaadi , apni londi se kar dey to phir wo us (londi) ke parde ki jagah ko na dekhey.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''wo zere-naaf aur ghutnon ke ooper ke hissey ko na dekhey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3112,Hazrat jarhad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumhen malum nahin ke raan parda (yani sattar) hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood.
3113,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''Ali ! tum apni raan zahir karo na kisi zinda aur murda ki raan ko dekho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja.
3114,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Maamer (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se guzrey to unki dono raanein nangi thin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Maamer ! apni raanein dhaanpo, kyonkey raanein sattar hain.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
3115,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nangey honey se bacho, kyonkey tumharey sath wo (farishtey) hain jo tumharey sath hi rehtey hain, aur wo sirf us waqt judaa hotey hain jab aadmi baitul-khala (toilet) jata hai aur jab apni ehliya se talluq zinsi taaluq karta hai, tum un se haya karo aur unki takrim (izzat) karo.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3116,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke wo aur Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas thin ke itney mein ibne Umme-Maktum (Raziallahu anhu) aaye aur aap ki khidmat mein hazir huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum dono is se parda karo.'' maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya wo na-bina nahin? wo hamein dekh nahin sakta, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum dono na-bina ho ! tum usey nahin dekh rahi ho.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
3117,"Hazrat Behaz bin Haakim apney walid se aur wo uskey dada (Muawiya bin Hewa) se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni ehliya (biwi) ya apni londi ke ilawa apney sattar ki hifazat kar.'' maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey bataeyn ke jab aadmi tanhai mein ho (phir bhi) ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah uska ziyada haq daar hai ke us se haya ki jaey.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3118,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi aadmi kisi (ajnabi) aurat ke sath alehdgi mein hota hai to un dono ka teesra shetan hota hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3119,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jin (ajnabi) aurton ke khawind (shohar) mojud na hon tum unke paas na jaao, kyonkey shetan tum mein dorane khoon ki tarah gardish karta hai.'' ham ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! aap mein bhi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(haan) aur mujh mein bhi, lekin Allah ne uskey khilaf meri madad farmaee to wo Mutee ho gaya / main mehfooz rehta hun.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3120,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik ghulam lekar Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tashrif laye jisey aapney unhen hiba kar diya tha, Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) par eik kapda tha, jab Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) us se apna sar dhaanptin to wo aap ke paaon tak na pahunchta, aur jab wo us se apney paaon dhaanptin to wo unke sar tak na pahunchta, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unki is pareshani aur takleef ko dekha to farmaya : ''tum par koi harj nahin, in , main se eik tumharey walid hain aur doosra tumhara ghulam hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3121,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke paas tashrif farma they jabkey ghar main eik mukhannas tha, usney Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke bhai Abdullah bin Ubai Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : Abdullah ! agar Allah ne kal tumhen Taaif mein Fateh ata ki to main tumhen Ghelaan ki eik ladki bataaunga wo jab samney aati hai to uskey pet par chaar bal padtey hain aur jab mud'ti hai to is par aath bal padtey hain. is par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye (mukhannas) log tumharey paas na aaya keren.'' muttafaq aleh."
3122,"Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine eik bhari patthar uthaya hua tha aur usi haalat mein chal raha tha ke mera kapda gir gaya (jis se sattar khul gaya), main usey utha na saka , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey dekha to farmaya : ''apney ooper kapda lo aur uriyaan (nangi) haalat mein na chalo.'' rawahu Muslim."
3123,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sharm-gah kabhi nahin dekhi. rawahu ibne-Maja."
3124,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo musalman pehli martaba kisi aurat ke Husn aur jamaal par nazar daalta hai aur phir wo apni nazar jhuka leta hai to Allah usey eik aisi ibadat ki tofiq ata farmata hai jiski wo halaawat (mithaas) mehsus karta hai.'' rawahu Ahmed."
3125,Hazrat Hasan Basri (Raziallahu anhu) mursal riwayat kartey hain ke mujhey riwayat pahunchi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah sattar dekhney waley aur sattar dikhaney waley par lanat farmaey.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan).
3126,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bewa aurat ka nikah na kiya jaey jab tak us se mushaawarat na kar li jaey, aur kanwari aurat ka nikah na kiya jaey jab tak us se ijazat na li jaey.'' Sahaba kiram ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! aur uski ijazat kis tarah hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uska khamosh rehna ijazat hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3127,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bewa apni zaat ke barey mein apney wali se ziyada haq daar hai. jabkey kanwari se uski zaat ke barey mein ijazat talab ki jaeygi, aur uska khamosh rehna uski ijazat hai.'' eik riwayat mein hai aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bewa apni zaat ke barey mein apney wali se ziyada haq daar hai jabkey kanwari se ijazat talab ki jaeygi aur uska khamosh rehna uski ijazat hai.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bewa apni zaat ke barey mein apney wali se ziyada haq daar hai, jabkey kanwari ke mutalliq uska walid us se ijazat talab kerega aur uska khamosh rehna uski ijazat hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3128,Hazrat Khansa binte Khizaam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo bewa thin aur unke walid ne unki shaadi kar di. Khansa ne usey napasand kiya to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aayen to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unka nikah fasakh (radd) kar diya. Bukhari. aur ibne-Maja ki riwayat mein hai : uskey walid ka kiya hua nikah fasakh (radd) kar diya.
3129,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se shaadi ki to unki umr saat baras thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ghar unki rukhsati hui tab unki umr no baras thi aur unke khiloney unke sath they, aur jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wafat pai to unki umr atthaara baras thi. rawahu Muslim."
3130,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wali ke baghair nikah nahin.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
3131,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo aurat apney wali ki ijazat ke baghair apna nikah karey to uska nikah batil hai, uska nikah batil hai, uska nikah batil hai. agar us (mard) ne us se jima (sambhog) kiya hai to wo mehar ki haq daar hai kyonkey usney us se mubashrat ki hai, agar wo (wali) ikhtilaf karen to jis ka wali na ho to sultan (badshah) uska wali hai.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
3132,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''zaaniya wo hain jo gawah ke baghair apna nikah keren.'' durust baat ye hai ke ye ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ka qol hai. rawahu Tirmizi.
3133,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yateem ladki se uski zaat ke barey mein ijazat li jaeygi, agar wo khamosh rahey to phir yehi uski ijazat hai, aur agar wo inkar kar dey to phir is par ziyadti na ki jaey.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3134,Hazrat Imam Darmi ne usey Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Darmi.
3135,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo ghulam apney aaqa ki ijazat ke baghair shaadi karey to wo zaani hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Darmi."
3136,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik naabaaligha ladki Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur usney arz kiya ke uskey walid ne uski shaadi kar di hai jabke wo usey napasand karti hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey (shaadi barqarar rakhney ya fasakh (radd) karney ka ( ikhtiyar diya."
3137,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi aurat dusri aurat ka nikah na kiraaey aur na koi aurat khud apna nikah kiraaey kyonkey wo zaaniya hai jo apna nikah khud karti hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
3138,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis ke yahan bachcha paida ho to usey chahiye ke wo uska achchha naam rakhey , usey adab sikhaey aur jab wo baligh ho jaey to uski shaadi kar dey , agar wo baligh ho jaey aur wo (walid) uski shaadi na karey aur wo kisi gunah (zina waghera) ka irtikab kar ley to uska gunah uskey walid par hai.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
3139,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) aur Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Taurat mein likha hua hai, jis shakhs ki beti baara baras ki ho jaey aur wo uski shaadi na karey aur wo (ladki) kisi gunah ka irtikab kar ley to uska gunah uskey walid par hai.'' Behaqi ne ye dono riwaayatein Shobil-emaan mein bayan kin hain. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
3140,"Hazrat Rubayyea binte-Muawwiz bin Ifra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, jab mujhey shaadi ke baad merey khawind ke ghar laya gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur merey bistar par is tarah beth gaey jis tarah aap (hadees ke raawi Khalid bin Zakwaan) mujh se (door) bethey hain, isliye ansaar ki chhoti chhoti bachchiyaan daf baja kar merey un baap-daada jo ghazwae uhad mein Shahid ho gaey they, ki khoobiyon ko bayan karney lagin, ke achcha un mein se eik ne keh diya : ham main eik Nabi hain, jo mustaqbil ke waqiyat jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isey chhodo, aur jo tum pehley keh rahi thin wohi kaho.'' Bukhari."
3141,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, eik aurat ki eik Ansari sahabi ke sath rukhsati hui to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumharey paas khel kood ka saman nahin tha? kyonkey ansaar ko daf aur ashaar kehna achchha lagta hai.'' Bukhari."
3142,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne shawwaal mein mujh se shaadi ki aur shawwaal mein mujhey apney ghar laye aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki paak biviyon (biwiyon) mein se kon si wo biwi hai jisey aap ke yahan mujh se aham maqam hasil tha? rawahu Muslim."
3143,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jin sharton ke sath tum ne sharam-gaahon ko halal banaya hai, wo (sharten) ziyada haq rakhti hain ke unhen pura kiya jaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
3144,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aadmi apney (musalman) bhai ke peghame nikah par peghame nikah na bhejey yahan tak ke wo nikah kar ley ya chhod dey.'' muttafaq aleh."
3145,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aurat apni (musalman) behan ki Talaq ka mutalba na karey taake usey uska rizq bhi mil jaey usey chahiye ke wo us mard se khud shaadi kar ley, halanke jo uskey muqaddar mein hai wo usey mil jaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
3146,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ''nikahe-shighaar'' se mana farmaya hai. aur shighaar ye hai ke aadmi apni beti ki shaadi is shart par karey ke doosra aadmi apni beti ki shaadi us se kar dey aur un dono ke darmiyan mehar na ho.'' aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Islam mein shighaar nahin.'' muttafaq aleh.
3147,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghazwae-khaibar ke moqe par aurton se mut'aa karney aur gharelu gadhon ka gosht khaney se mana farmaya. muttafaq aleh.
3148,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghazwae-autaas ke moqe par teen roz ke liye mut'aa ki ijazat di phir us se mana farma diya. rawahu Muslim."
3149,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein Namaz mein tashahud padhna sikhai aur zarurat (nikah waghera) mein tashahud sikhai, raawi bayan kartey hain, Namaz mein tashahud ke alfaz ye hain : (التَّحِيَّاتُ لِلَّهِ وَالصَّلَوَاتُ وَالطَّيِّبَاتُ ، السَّلَامُ عَلَيْكَ أَيُّهَا النَّبِيُّ وَرَحْمَةُ اللَّهِ وَبَرَكَاتُهُ ، السَّلَامُ عَلَيْنَا وَعَلَى عِبَادِ اللَّهِ الصَّالِحِينَ ، أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَأَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ وَرَسُولُهُ) ''zabaani, badani aur maali ibadaten Allah ke liye hain, aey Nabi ! aap par salamti, Allah ki rehmat aur uski barkat hon, ham par aur Allah ke nek bandon par salamti ho, main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain.'' aur kisi hajat aur zarurat ke waqt padha janey wala tashahud ye hai : (اِنَّ الْحَمْدَ لِلہِ نَسْتَعِیْنُہ وَنَسْتَغْفِرُہ وَنَعُوْذُ بِاللہِ مِنْ شُرُوْرِ اَنْفُسِنَا , مِنْ یَّھْدِہِ اللہُ فَلَا مُضِلَّ لَہ , وَمَنْ یُّضْلِلْہُ فَلَا ھَادِیَ لَہ , وَاَشْھَدُ اَنْ لَّا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللہُ , وَاَشْھَدُ اَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُہ وَرَسُوْلُہ) ''be-shak her qism ki hamd Allah ke liye hai, ham usi se madad chahtey aur usi se maghfirat talab kartey hain, ham apney nafson ki buraiyon se Allah ki panah chahtey hain. jis ko Allah hidayat ata farma dey usey koi gumrah nahin kar sakta aur jisey wo gumrah kar dey usey koi hidayat deney wala nahin, aur main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye teen aayaat tilawat farmatey : (یَآ اَیُّھَا الَّذِیْنَ امَنُوا اتَّقُوا اللہَ حَقَّ تُقَاتِہِ وَلَا تَمُوْتُنَّ اِلَّا وَ اَنْتُمْ مُسْلِمُوْنَ) ''aey eman walo ! Allah se dar jaao jis tarah us se darney ka haq hai. aur tum us haal mein maro ke tum musalman ho.'' ( یَآیُّھَا النَّاسُ اتَّقُوْا رَبَّکُمُ الَّذِیْ خَلَقَکُمْ مَّنْ نَّفْسٍ وَّاحِدَۃٍ وَّ خَلَقَ مِنْھَا زَوْجَھَا وَبَثَّ مِنْھُمَا رِجَالًا کَثِیْرًا وَّنِسَآءً وَاتَّقُوا اللہَ الَّذِیْ تَسَآءَ لُوْنَ بِہِ وَالَا رْ حَامَ اِنَّ اللہَ کَانَ عَلَیْکُمْ رَقِیْبًا) ''aey logo ! apney rab se daro jisney tumhen eik shakhs (Hazrat Adam (Alaihissalam)) se paida kiya, aur usi se uska joda banaya , phir un dono se badi tadaad mein mard aur aurten paida karkey unhen roey zamin par phela diya aur daro Allah se jiskey zariey tum apni zarooriyaat zindagi puri kartey ho, aur qata' rehmi se bacho. Allah Taala yaqinan tumhen dekh raha hai.'' (یَآ اَیُّھَا الَّذِیْ امَنُوا اتَّقُوا اللہَ وَقُوْلُوْا قَوْلًا سَدِیْدًا یُّصْلِحْ لکُمْ اَعْمَالکُمْ وَیَغْفِرْلکُمْ ذُنُوْبَکُمْ وَمَنْ یُّطِعِ اللہَ وَرَسُوْلَہ فَقَدْ فَازَ فَوْزًا عَظِیْمًا) ''aey eman walo ! Allah se daro aur durust baat karo, wo tumharey aamaal durust kar dega aur tumharey gunah bakhsh dega. aur jo shakhs Allah aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki itaat karey wo bahut badi kamiyabi hasil kar lega.'' aur Jaame Tirmizi mein hai. Sufiyan Sauri ne teeno aayaat ki wazahat ki. aur ibne-Maja ne (اِنَّ الْحَمْدَ لِلہِ) ke baad (نَحْمَدُہُ) aur (مِنْ شُرُوْرِ اَنْفُسِنَا) ke baad (وَمِنْ سَیَّئَاتِ اَعْمَالِنَا) ka izafa naqal kiya aur Darmi ne (عَظِیْمًا) ke baad izafa naqal kiya hai ke phir apni hajat aur zarurat ka tazkira karey. aur Sharahus-sunnah mein ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke is tashahud ko nikah ke khutba hajat ya kisi doosrey khutbe mein padhey. (rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, Nasai, ibne-Maja, Darmi aur fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
3150,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her wo khutba jis mein tashahud (hamd aur sanaa) na ho to wo katey huey haath ki tarah hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3151,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her aham kaam jis ka aaghaz Allah ki hamd se na kiya jaey wo (kaam) barkat se khaali hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
3152,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nikah ka aelan karo aur usey masjid mein karo, aur us moqe par daf bajaoo.'' Tirmizi. aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3153,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Haatib Jamhi (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nikah ke moqe par (nikah ki) tashheer aur daf bajana (nikah) halal aur haram mein farq karta hai.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi, Nasai aur ibne-Maja."
3154,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, merey paas ansaar ki eik ladki thi, maine uski shaadi kar di, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Aaisha ! tum ashaar ka intizam kyon nahin karti, kyonkey ansaar ka ye qabila ashaar pasand karta hai.'' (rawahu ibne-Hibban fi sahi)."
3155,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne ansaar mein se apni eik Azeeza ki shaadi ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur farmaya : ''kya tum ne ladki ko bhej diya?'' unhoney arz kiya : ji haan, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne ashaar padhney walon ko uskey sath bheja hai? ''Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : nahin, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ansaar aisey log hain jo gaaney ka rujhaan rakhtey hain, agar tum uskey sath kisi aisey shakhs ko bhejti jo kehta : (اَتَیْنا کُمْ اَتَیْنَا کُمْ فَحَیَّانَا وَ حَیَّاکُمْ) ham tumharey paas aaye , ham tumharey paas aaye hamein bhi Mubarak ho aur tumhen bhi Mubarak ho'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
3156,"Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis aurat ki shaadi do wali kar den to wo un dono mein se pehley waley ke nikah mein hogi. aur jo shakhs do aadmiyon se bai (khareed farokht) karey to wo un mein se pehley ke liye hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, Nasai aur Darmi."
3157,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath jihad mein shareek hotey they aur hamarey sath aurten nahin hoti thin, ham ne arz kiya : kya ham khassi na ho jaeyn? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein is se mana farmaya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein mut'aa karney ki rukhsat (chhoot) ata farmaee, ham mein se koi shakhs kapdey ke iwaz eik muddat tak kisi aurat se nikah karta, phir Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''aey momino ! pakizah chizon ko, jo Allah ne tumharey liye halal ki hain, haram qarar na do.'' muttafaq aleh."
3158,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, mut'aa Islam ke ibtidaai (shuruati) daur mein tha wo is tarah ke, aadmi shehar mein jata, uski wahan jaan pehchan na hoti to wo wahan apney qiyam ke andazey ke mutabiq aurat se shaadi kar leta to wo uskey saman ki hifazat karti aur uskey liye khana tayyar karti yahan tak ke jab ye aayat nazil hui : ''magar apni biwiyon par ya apni laundiyon par.'' ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ''un dono (biwi aur londi) ki sharm-gah ke siwa her sharm-gah haraam hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3159,"Hazrat Aamir bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main eik shaadi ke moqe par Qurza bin Kab aur Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya to dekha ke chhoti bachchiyaan ga rahi thin, maine kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sathiyo aur Badr ke ghaaziyo ! tumharey paas ye ho raha hai? un dono ne farmaya : agar tum chaho to hamarey paas beth kar suno aur agar tum chaho to jaao , kyonkey shaadi ke moqe par gaaney ke mutalliq hamein ijazat di gaee hai. rawahu Nasai."
3160,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aurat aur uski phuphi isi ke saath aurat aur uski khaala ko nikah mein ikhatta na kiya jaey.'' (yani phuphi, bhatij aur khaala bhaanji, eik waqt main eik aadmi ki biwiyan nahin ho saktin) muttafaq aleh."
3161,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''doodh peeney se wo rishtey haram ho jatey hain, jo nasab se haram hotey hain.'' Bukhari."
3162,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, merey razaai (doodh-shareek) chacha aaye , unhoney merey paas aaney ki ijazat talab ki to maine unhen ijazat deney se inkar kar diya yahan tak ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se daryaft kar lun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye, maine aap se puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba wo tumhara chacha hai lihaza usey ijazat dey do.'' wo bayan karti hain, maine aap se arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey to aurat ne doodh pilaya hai, mard ne to mujhey doodh nahin pilaya ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba wo tumhara chacha hai. lihaza wo tumharey paas aa sakta hai.'' aur ye ham par parda ke ehkam nazil honey se baad ka waqia hai. muttafaq aleh."
3163,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya aap apney chacha Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti ke barey mein raghbat rakhtey hain? wo Quraish ki sab se ziyada Husain aur jameel ladki hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''kya tumhen malum nahin ke Hamza merey razaai bhai hain, aur Allah ne razaat ki wajeh se wo rishtey haram kiye hain, jo usney nasab ki wajeh se haram kiye hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
3164,Hazrat Umme-Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik martaba ya do martaba doodh peena hurmat Sabit nahin karta.'' rawahu Muslim.
3165,Aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hadees mein hai : ''eik martaba aur do martaba doodh choosney se hurmat waqey nahin hoti.'' rawahu Muslim.
3166,Aur Umme-Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) dusri hadees mein hai : ''eik ya do martaba doodh peeney se hurmat waqey nahin hoti.'' teeno riwayaat Sahih Muslim ki hain. rawahu Muslim.
3167,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Quran mein ye hukm nazil hua tha ke das martaba doodh peeney se hurmat waqey hoti hai. phir wo hukm paanch martaba peeney ki qaid ke sath mansookh kar diya gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jis waqt wafat pai to us waqt tak (paanch martaba doodh peeney wali aayat) Quran mein padhi jati thi. rawahu Muslim."
3168,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye to merey paas eik aadmi tha, goya aapney usey napasand farmaya , Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne arz kiya, ye to mera bhai hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dekho ke tumharey bhai kon hain, razaat (doodh-shareek) to sirf wo doodh hai jisey bhook door karney ke liye piya gaya ho.'' (bachchey ko kam Umari mein bhook lagi ho aur wo kisi aurat ka doodh pi ley) muttafaq aleh."
3169,"Hazrat Aqba bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Abu-Abaab bin Aziz ki beti se shaadi kar li to eik aurat aai, usney kaha : maine Aqba aur uski biwi ko doodh pilaya hai. (yani ye aapas mein razaai (doodh-shareek) behan bhai hain) Aqba ne us aurat se kaha : mujhey to malum nahin ke tum ne mujhey doodh pilaya hai aur na hi tum ne mujhey bataya hai. unhoney Abu-Abaab ke ghar walon ke paas kisi aadmi ko bheja to usney un se puchha to unhoney kaha : hamen to malum nahin ke usney hamari is ladki ko doodh pilaya hai, wo Madina mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(tum uskey sath) kis tarah (talluq qaaim kar saktey ho) halanke ye keh diya gaya (ke tum uskey razaai (doodh-shareek) bhai ho).'' Aqba (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey alag kar diya aur usney unke ilawa kisi aur se nikah kiya. Bukhari."
3170,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hunain ke din Autas ki taraf eik lashkar rawana kiya to unka dushman se aamna samna hua, unhoney un se qitaal kiya aur wo un par ghalib aagey aur unhoney kuch khawatin giraftar kar lein, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baaz Sahaba ne un laundiyon se unke mushrik khaawindon ke mojud honey ki wajeh sey, jima (sambhog) karney mein harj mehsus kiya to Allah Taala ne uskey mutalliq ye aayat nazil farmaai : ''aur shaadi shuda aurten (tum par haram ki gaee hain) magar tumhari londiyan.'' yani jab unki iddat mukammal ho jaey to phir wo tumharey liye halal hain. rawahu Muslim."
3171,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke aisi aurat se nikah kiya jaey jiski phuphi uskey nikah mein pehley se ho ya phuphi se uski bhatiji ke hotey huey nikah na kiya jaey, isi tarah khaala aur bhaanji ko ya bhaanji aur khaala ko eik sath eik mard ke nikah mein jama na kiya jaey isi ke saath (rishtey mein) chhoti (maslan : bhatiji, bhaanji) ka badi par aur aur badi ka chhoti par nikah karney se mana farmaya. Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Darmi aur Nasai. aur unki riwayat (binte Ukhtaha) tak hai. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, Darmi aur Nasai."
3172,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, merey mamu Abu-Burda bin Niyar (Raziallahu anhu) parcham uthaey merey paas se guzrey to maine kaha : aap kahan ja rahey hain? unhoney kaha : mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ki taraf bheja hai, jisney apney baap ki biwi se shaadi ki hai, taake main uska sar aap ki khidmat mein pesh karun. isey Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood ne riwayat kiya hai, Abu-Dawud, Nasai , ibne-Maja aur Darmi ki riwayat mein hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey hukm farmaya hai ke main usey qatl kar dun aur uska maal ley lun. aur us riwayat mein ''merey mamu'' ke bajaey ''merey chacha'' ka lafz hai. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, Nasai, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
3173,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo razaat (doodh pilana) baaise hurmat hai, jo barahe-rast chhaatiyon se doodh pi kar (bhook mita kar) antadiyaan khol dey, aur ye (raza'at) doodh chudaney se pehley ho.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3174,"Hazrat Hujjaj bin Hujjaj Aslami apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! mujhse kis tarah doodh pilane ka haq ada ho sakta hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' razaai (doodh-shareek) maa ko ghulam ya londi deney se.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, Nasai aur Darmi ."
3175,"Hazrat Abu-Tufail Ghanwi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha ke eik aurat aai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni chadar bichhaai yahan tak ke wo is par beth gaee, jab wo chali gaee to bataya gaya ke us khatoon ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko doodh pilaya tha (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki razaai (doodh-shareek) walida hain). rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3176,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Ghelaan bin Salma Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) ne Islam qubul kiya aur unki daure jahiliyat mein das biwiyan thin, wo bhi unke sath hi musalman ho gaeen, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chaar rakh lo aur baqi farigh kar do.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
3177,"Hazrat Nofal bin Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Islam qubul kiya to us waqt meri paanch biwiyan thin, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik ko chhod do aur chaar rakh lo.'' maine un mein se apni sab se pehli biwi ko, jo baanjh thi aur saath saal se meri rafeeqe-hayaat thi, khud se juda kar diya. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
3178,"Hazrat Suhak bin Feeroz Dailmi apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! maine Islam qubul kar liya hai aur do behney merey nikah mein hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''un dono mein se jisey chaho ikhtiyar kar lo (doosri chhod do).'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3179,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aurat ne Islam qubul kiya aur usney shaadi kar li, itney mein uska (pehla) khawind Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! main Islam qubul kar chuka hun aur us (aurat) ko merey Islam qubul karney ka ilm hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us (aurat) ko uskey doosrey khawind se lekar uskey pehley khawind ko wapis kar diya. aur eik riwayat mein hai ke usney arz kiya is (aurat) ne merey sath hi Islam qubul kya hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us (aurat) ko uskey hawaley kar diya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3180,"Hazrat Sharahus-sunnah mein marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kitni hi aurton ko pehley nikah par hi unke khaawindon ki taraf lauta diya jab unhoney Islam qubul kar liya agar-che eik waqt tak unka Deen aur rehan-sahan eik doosrey se alag raha, un mein Waleed bin Mughira ki beti hain jo ke Safwan bin Umayya ke nikah mein thin, Fateh Makka ke roz wo to musalman ho gaeen jabkey unka khawind Islam qubul karney se bhag gaya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey chacha Zaad Wahab bin Umer ko Safwan ki aman ke liye apni chadar de-kar bheja , jab wo aaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey chaar maah ghoomney phirney ki mohlat ata ki yahan tak ke usney Islam qubul kar liya to wo (Waleed bin Mughira ki beti) uskey nikah mein rahin, aur (isi tarah) Ikrima bin Abi Jahal ki biwi Umme-Haakim binte Haris bin Hisham ne Fateh Makka ke roz Islam qubul kar liya jabkey uska khawind Islam se bhag kar Yamen chala gaya to Umme-Haakim ne bhi kooch kiya yahan tak ke uskey paas Yamen pahunch gaeen aur usey Islam ki dawat pesh ki to usney Islam qubul kar liya, aur dono ka nikah barqarar raha. Imam Maalik ne ibne-Shahab se mursal riwayat kiya hai. (rawahu Maalik aur fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
3181,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, saat rishtey nasab ki wajeh se haram hain aur saat nikah ki wajeh se. phir unhoney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''tum par tumhari maaeyn haram kar di gaee hain.'' Bukhari."
3182,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis aadmi ne kisi aurat se nikah kiya aur us se sohbat ki to phir uskey liye us aurat ki beti se nikah karna halal nahin, aur agar usney uskey sath jinsi talluq qaaim nahin kiya to phir wo uski beti se nikah kar sakta hai. aur jis aadmi ne kisi aurat se nikah kiya to phir ab uskey liye uski maa se nikah karna halal nahin chahey (chaahe) usney us se jinsi talluq qaaim kiya ho ya na kiya ho.'' Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye hadees sanad ke hawaley se sahih nahin, ibne-Lahiyaa aur Musanna bin Sabaah ne usey Amr bin Shuaib se riwayat kiya hai, aur un dono ko hadees mein zaeef qarar diya gaya hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3183,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, yahood kaha kartey they, jab aadmi apni biwi se uski pichli janib se uski agli jagah mein jima (sambhog) karey to bachcha bhengaa paida hota hai. is par ye aayat nazil hui : ''tumhari aurten tumhari kheti hain, tum jaisey chaho apni kheti ko aao.'' muttafaq aleh."
3184,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham azl kiya kartey they jabkey Quran nazil ho raha tha. Bukhari , Muslim . aur Imam Muslim ne mazeed ye bhi riwayat kiya hai ke ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tak pahunchi to aapney hamein mana nahin farmaya. muttafaq aleh."
3185,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney arz kiya : meri eik londi hai wo hamari khaadima hai aur main us se jima (sambhog) karta hun jabkey main napasand karta hun ke wo hamila ho, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum chaho to us se azl (sambhog is trah se ke mani sharm-gaah me na gire) karo, kyonkey jo uskey muqaddar mein hai wo usey mil kar rahega.'' kuchh muddat guzri to wo aadmi phir aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney arz kiya : londi to hamila ho gaee hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine tumhen bata diya tha ke uskey muqaddar mein jo kuchh hai wo usey mil kar rahega.'' rawahu Muslim."
3186,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ghazwae bani mustaliq mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein rawana huey to kuchh Arab londiyan hamarey haath lagin, hamein aurton ki raghbat hui aur aurton se alag rehna hamarey liye dushwaar ho gaya aur ham ne azl (sambhog is trah se ke mani sharm-gaah me na gire) karna pasand kiya, ham ne azl karney ka irada kiya aur ham ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se daryaft kiye baghair azl kartey hain jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ham mein mojud hain, ham ne uskey mutalliq aap se masla puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya harj hai ! agar tum aisey na karo? kyonkey jis jaan ne qiyamat tak aana hai usney aana hi hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3187,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se azl (sambhog is trah se ke mani sharm-gaah me na gire) ke mutalliq puchha gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her pani (mani) se bachcha nahin hota, aur jab Allah kisi chiz ki takhleeq ka irada farmata hai to phir koi chiz usey rok nahin sakti.'' rawahu Muslim."
3188,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. usney arz kiya : main apni biwi se azl (sambhog is trah se ke mani sharm-gaah me na gire) karta hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se puchha : ''tum ye kyon kartey ho?'' us aadmi ne arz kiya : mujhey uskey bachchey (hamal ya sher khuwar) ke mutalliq andesha hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar ye (jimaa) Muzar hota to ye faarsiyon aur roomiyon ke liye Muzar hota .'' rawahu Muslim."
3189,"Hazrat Juzaama binte Wahab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, main kuchh logon ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui us waqt aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma rahey they.'' maine ''Ghailaa'' (haalate-hamal mein doodh pilaney) ne mana karney ka irada kiya, phir maine roomiyon aur faarsiyon ko dekha ke wo apni aulad ko haalate hamal mein doodh pilaatey rehtey hain, aur ye unki aulad ko kuch bhi nuqsan nahin pahunchata.'' phir unhoney aap se azl (sambhog is trah se ke mani sharm-gaah me na gire) ke mutalliq puchha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye (azl karna) insan ko zinda dargor (qabr mein dafan) karna hai. aur ye (azl karna) Allah ke us farman : ''jab zinda dargor ki gaee bachchi se puchha jaeyga.'' ke zamra mein aata hai. rawahu Muslim."
3190,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat Allah ke yahan sab se badi amanat '' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''roze-qiyamat Allah ke nazdik us aadmi ka maqam sab se bura hoga jo apni ehliya ke paas jata hai aur wo uskey paas jati hai, phir wo aadmi us (ehliya) ke raz afshaan (faash) kar deta hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3191,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf ""wahi"" ki gaee : ''tumhari aurten tumhari kheti hain, tum apni kheti ko aao.'' ''samney se aao ya pichli taraf se aao lekin peeth mein (lawaatat) aur haalate haiz mein jima (sambhog) karney se bacho.'' rawahu Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
3192,"Hazrat Khuzaima bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah bayane-haq se nahin sharmata, tum aurton se unki peeth mein mubashrat (sambhog) na karo.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
3193,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apni ehliya ke paas maqad (peeth) mein aaye wo maloon (laanat ke qabil) hai.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
3194,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apni ehliya se uski peeth se aata hai to Allah uski taraf nazar (rehmat) nahin farmaeyga.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
3195,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah us shakhs ki taraf nazar (rehmat) nahin farmaeyga jo kisi mard ya kisi aurat se lawaatat (sambhog peeth ki janib se) karta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3196,"Hazrat Asma binte Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''apni aulad ko poshida taur par qatl na karo, kyonkey'' hamila aurat ka doodh achchha ghod sawar nahin banney deta aur usey uskey ghodey se pachhaad deta hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3197,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne azad aurat se uski ijazat ke baghair azl (sambhog is trah se ke mani sharm-gaah me na gire) karney se mana farmaya. rawahu ibne-Maja."
3198,"Hazrat Urwa, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ke barey mein unhen farmaya : ''usey (uskey malikon sey) lekar azad kar do.'' aur uska khawind ghulam tha lihaza Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (nikah barqarar rakhney ya fasakh (radd) karney ka ( usey ikhtiyar diya to usney apney nikah ko fasakh kar diya, aur agar wo (Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ka khaawind) azad hota to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usko ikhtiyar na detey. muttafaq aleh."
3199,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ke khawind (shohar) siyah faam (rang) ghulam they unhen Mughis ke naam se yad kiya jata tha, ab bhi mujhey aisa lagta hai ke main usey Madina ki galiyon mein us (Barira) ke peechey peechey chakkar kaat'taa dekh raha hun, uskey aansu uski dadhi par rawan hain, (ye sooratehaal dekh kar) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''Abbas ! kya tumhen Mughis ki Barira se mohabbat aur Barira ki Mughis se nafrat se tajjub nahin ho raha?'' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (Barira sey) farmaya : ''agar tum uskey nikah mein rehney ka dobara faisla kar lo?'' usney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! aap mujhey hukm farma rahey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main to mehaz sifarish karta hun.'' usney kaha : mujhey is mein koi raghbat nahin. Bukhari."
3200,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke unhoney apney do ghulam, jo ke miyan biwi they, azad karney ka irada kiya aur unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se daryaft kiya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen hukm farmaya ke mard ko aurat se pehley azad karo. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3201,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Barira (Raziallahu anhu) azad ki gaee to wo us waqt Mughis (Raziallahu anhu) ke nikah mein thin, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey ikhtiyar diya aur usey farmaya : ''agar usney tum se (azadi ke doran) jima kar liya to phir tera ikhtiyar khatam ho jaeyga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3202,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui to usney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! maine apney aap ko aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye hiba kiya, wo der tak khadi rahi , to eik aadmi khada hua, usney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! agar aap is mein raghbat nahin rakhtey to phir is se meri shaadi kar den. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya usey mehar deney ke liye tumharey paas kuchh hai?'' usney arz kiya : merey paas to sirf meri ye chadar hi hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''talash karo chahey (chaahe) lohey ki eik anguthi hi ho.'' usney talash kiya lekin usney kuchh na paya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumhen Quran ka kuchh hissey yad hai? '' usney arz kiya : ji haan , falan falan surat. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine Quran ke is hissey ke zariey jo tumhen yad hai tumhari us se shaadi kar di.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''jaao ! maine tumhari us se shaadi kar di, usey Quran (ka wo hissey jo tumhen yad hai) sikha do.'' muttafaq aleh."
3203,"Hazrat Abu-Salma bayan kartey hain, maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke haq mehar ki miqdaar kitni thi? unhoney farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki paak biviyon ke haq mehar ki miqdaar baara auqiya aur eik nash thi. phir unhoney farmaya : kya tum jantey ho ke ''nash'' kya hai? maine kaha : nahin, unhoney farmaya : nisf (aadha) auqiya, aur ye (baara auqiya aur nash) paanch so dirham hain. Muslim, aur nash, Sharahus-sunnah aur deegar tamam masaadir mein rafa' (door) ke sath hai. rawahu Muslim aur Sharahus-sunnah."
3204,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, sun lo ! aurton ke mehar ka haq ziyada muqarrar na karo, kyonkey wo duniya mein qabile-izzat aur Allah ke yahan baaise-taqwa hota to tumhari nisbat Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey ziyada haq daar they, mein nahin janta ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne paak biviyon (Raziallahu anhu) se nikah kiya ho ya apni betiyon ka nikah kiya ho to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne baara auqiya se ziyada mehar ka haq muqarrar kiya ho. rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, Nasai, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
3205,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne apni ehliya ko dono haath bhar kar sattu ya khajoor bator mehar ada kiya to usney (us aurat ko) apney liye jayez kar liya.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood.
3206,"Hazrat Aamir bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke bano Fazara qabiley ki eik aurat ne jooton ke jodey ke iwaz shaadi kar li to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''kya tum khud ko aur apney maal ko jooton ke jodey ke iwaz deney par razi ho?'' usney arz kiya : ji haan, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us (nikah) ko nafiz (laagu) farma diya. rawahu Tirmizi."
3207,"Hazrat Alqama , ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke un se eik aadmi ke mutalliq puchha gaya jisney kisi aurat se shaadi ki aur usney uska haq mehar muqarrar nahin kiya aur na us se jima (sambhog) kiya yahan tak ke wo faut ho gaya, to ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya is aurat ko uskey khandan ki aurton ki jaisa haq mehar milega is mein koi kami beshi nahin hogi, wo iddat guzaarey gi aur meeras hasil karegi. (ye sun kar) Maaqil bin Sanan Ashjai khadey huey aur kaha : ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamarey khandan ki Birwa binte Washiq naami eik aurat ke mutalliq isi tarah faisla farmaya tha jaisey aapney faisla farmaya, to is par ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) khush huey. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, Nasai aur Darmi."
3208,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo Abdullah bin Jahash ke nikah mein thin, wo sarzameene Habsha mein intiqal kar gaey to Najashi ne unka Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se nikah kar diya aur unhen apni taraf se chaar hazar aur eik riwayat mein hai : chaar hazar dirham haq mehar ada kiya aur unhen Shurehbil bin Hasna ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3209,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne Umme Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) se shaadi ki to un dono ke darmiyan haq mehar Islam tha, umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) se pehley Islam qubul kar liya to Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen peghame nikah bheja jis par unhoney kaha : maine to Islam qubul kar liya hai, agar tum bhi Islam qubul kar lo to main tum se nikah kar lungi. (aur main haq mehar nahin lungi) unhoney Islam qubul kar liya aur yehi un dono ke darmiyan haq mehar tha. rawahu Nasai."
3210,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu)) ke badan ya kapdey ( par Zaafran ka nishan dekha to farmaya : ''ye kya hai? '' unhoney arz kya : maine paanch dirham ke iwaz eik aurat se shaadi ki hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah tumhen barkat ata farmaai , waleema karo chahey eik bakri hi ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
3211,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zenab (Raziallahu anhu) ki shaadi par jaisa waleema kya wesa waleema apni kisi zauja mohtarma ki shaadi par nahin kya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik bakri se waleema kya. muttafaq aleh."
3212,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) se shauhar-bevi wala talluq qaaim kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne waleema kya aur logon ko gosht roti se pet bhar diya. Bukhari ."
3213,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko azad kya aur un se shaadi ki aur unki azadi ko unka mehar muqarrar kya aur hees ( khajoor , paneer aur ghi se tayyar shuda halwa ( se unka waleema kya. muttafaq aleh."
3214,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar aur Madina ke darmiyan teen raaten qiyam farmaya, aapney Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath shauhar bivi wala talluq qaaim kya to maine musalmanon ko aap ke waleema ki dawat di, is mein roti thi na gosht, bas aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chamdey ki eik chatai mangaai, usey bicha diya gaya aur us (dasterkhaan) par khajoor, paneer aur ghi chun diya gaya. Bukhari."
3215,"Hazrat Safiya bint Sheba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni baaz biwiyon ka faqat do mud jo se waleema kya. Bukhari."
3216,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko dawate-walima di jaey to wo usey qubul kar ley.'' Bukhari, Muslim. aur Muslim ki eik riwayat mein hai : '' chahiye ke wo dawat qubul karey chahey shaadi ki dawat ho ya koi dusri dawat .'' muttafaq aleh."
3217,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko khaney ki dawat di jaey to wo is mein zarur shirkat karey, dil chahey to kha ley warna chhod dey.'' rawahu Muslim ."
3218,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sab se bura khana, walimey ka wo khana hai jismein maaldaaron ko bulaya jaey aur ghareebon ko chhod diya jaey, aur jisney dawat tarak ki to usney Allah aur uskey Rasool ki nafarmani ki.'' muttafaq aleh."
3219,"Hazrat abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ansaar ka eik aadmi tha jiski kunniyat abu-Shuaib thi, uska eik ghulam qassaab tha, usney kaha : merey liye khana tayyar karo jo ke paanch afrad ke liye kafi ho, taake main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dawat dun ke aap un mein se paanchwen hon, usney uskey liye mukhtasar sa khana tayyar kya, phir wo (abu-Shuaib) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap ko dawat di, to eik aur (chhata) aadmi unke sath aaney laga to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''abu-Shuaib! eik aur aadmi hamarey sath aa raha hai, agar tum chaho to usey ijazat dey do aur agar chaho to usey chhod do.'' usney arz kya : koi nahin! usey bhi ijazat hai. muttafaq aleh."
3220,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ka sattu aur khajoor se walima kya. rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja.
3221,"Hazrat Safina (Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke azad karda ghulam) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan mehman thehra to unhoney uskey liye khana tayyar kya, Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : agar ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bhi bula lein taake wo hamarey sath kha lein? unhoney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dawat di to aap tashrif laye aur aapney apney haath darwazey ki chaukhat par rakhey they ke ghar ki eik janib lagey huey naqshdar pardey ko dekha to aap wapis tashrif ley gaey. Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, main aap ke peechey gaee aur arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! kis chiz ne aap ko wapis kar diya? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey ya kisi Nabi ke liye laaiq nahin ke wo kisi muzayyan ghar mein dakhil ho.'' rawahu Ahmed w ibne-Maja ."
3222,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko dawat di jaey aur wo qubul na karey to usney Allah aur uskey Rasool ki nafarmani ki aur jo shakhs bin bulaey chala aaye to wo chor ki haisiyat se dakhil hua aur daku ki haisiyat se nikla.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3223,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke eik sahabi se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab dawat deney waley do afrad ikhattey ho jaeyn to phir un mein se jo padaus ke lihaz se ziyada qarib ho uski dawat qubul karo, aur agar un mein se koi eik sabqat ley jaey to phir us sabqat ley janey waley ki dawat qubul karo.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood."
3224,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''pehley din ( waleeme) ka khana haq ( wajib ( hai, doosrey roz dawat karna sunnat hai jabkey teesrey roz dawat karna shohrat w riya-kaari hai aur jo koi dikhawa karta hai to Allah ( qiyamat ke din ( usey ruswa kar dega .'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
3225,"Hazrat Ikrima, ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne baham (aapas mein) fakhr karney walon ka khana khaney se mana farmaya hai. Abu-Dawud ne farmaya : sahih ye hai ke Ikrima ki Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye mursal riwayat hai, rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3226,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do aapas mein fakhr karney walon ki dawat qubul na ki jaey aur na un dono ka khana khaya jaey.'' Imam Ahmed ne farmaya : yani wo do aadmi jo fakhr w riya ki khatir ziyaafat kartey hain. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
3227,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne fasiq logon ki dawat qubul karney se mana farmaya hai. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
3228,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi eik apney musalman bhai ke paas jaey to wo uskey khaney se khaye aur sawal na karey (ke ye kahan se aaya hai) aur wo uskey mashrub se piye aur kuch na poochey.'' Imam Behaqi ne ye teeno ahadis Shobil-emaan mein riwayat ki hain, aur farmaya : agar ye sahih hai, to zahir hai ke musalman usey sirf wohi chiz khilata pilata hai jo uskey nazdik halal hoti hai. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
3229,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wafat pai to us waqt aapki no paak biviyan thin, aur aapney un mein se aath ke liye baari muqarrar ki thi. muttafaq aleh."
3230,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke jab Sauda (Raziallahu anha) umr-raseeda (budhi) ho gaeen to unhoney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! aapki taraf se jo meri baari ka din tha wo maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko hiba kar diya, lihaza Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam), Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke liye do din taqseem farmaya kartey they, eik unka apna aur doosra Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ka din tha. muttafaq aleh."
3231,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney wafat key marz mein puchha kartey they, main kal kahan hunga? main kal kahan hunga? aap (us sawal sey) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki baari ka din poochhna chahtey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki paak biviyon ne aap ko ijazat de-di ke aap jahan chahen rahen, aap, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar they yahan tak ke aapney unke yahan hi wafat pai. Bukhari ."
3232,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) safar ka irada farmaya kartey they to aap apni azwaj (jodey) ke darmiyan qura andazi kya kartey they, jiskey naam qura nikalta to wo aap ke sath safar par rawana hoti thin. muttafaq aleh."
3233,"Hazrat abu-Qulaba, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : ''sunnat tariqa ye hai ke jab aadmi mutallaqa / bewa ke hotey huey kisi kanwari se shaadi karey to wo us ( kanwari (ke yahan saat raaten qiyam karey aur phir baari taqseem karey, aur jab bewa / mutallaqa se shaadi karey to uskey haan teen raaten qiyam karey aur phir baari taqseem karey. abu-Qulaba ne kaha : agar main chahun to main keh sakta hun ke Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se marfoo riwayat kya hai. muttafaq aleh."
3234,"Hazrat abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman se riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se shaadi ki aur wo aap ke yahan thehrin to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''aisi baat nahin hai ke teri merey yahan izzat nahin hai balke agar tum chaho to main tumharey yahan saat raaten qiyam karta hun aur phir main unke yahan bhi saat raaten qiyam karunga, aur agar tum chaho to main tumharey yahan teen raaten qiyam karta hun aur phir baaqiyon ke paas jata hun.'' unhon ( Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ( ne arz kya, aap teen raaten qiyam karen. aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : '' kanwari ke liye saat raaten hain aur bewa / mutallaqa ke liye teen raaten hain.'' rawahu Muslim ."
3235,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni paak biviyon ke darmiyan baari taqseem farmaya kartey they aur aap adl kya kartey they aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey they : ''aey Allah ! maine apni bisaat ke mutabiq baari taqseem kar rakhi hain, aap mujhey us chiz (yani dili mohabbat) ke barey mein malamat na karna jis ka tujhey ikhtiyar hai aur mujhey koi ikhtiyar nahin.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
3236,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis aadmi ki do biwiyan hun aur wo unke beech adl na karey to wo roze-qiyamat is haal mein hoga ke uska eik pehlu (nisf dhad) mafluj hoga.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
3237,"Hazrat Ata (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham maqam sarf par ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) ke janaazey mein shareek they, to unhoney farmaya : ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma hain, unhen jhatkey se nahin uthana aur na chaltey waqt jhatkey dena aur balke usey aaram se lekar chalna , kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki no biwiyan thin, aap un mein se aath ke liye baari muqarrar kartey they aur eik ke liye baari muqarrar nahin farmatey they, Ata bayan kartey hain, hamen ye baat pahunchi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jis paak bivi ke liye baari muqarrar nahin farmaya kartey they wo Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) thin, aur unhoney un mein se sab se aakhir mein Madina mein wafat pai . muttafaq aleh. rizeen ne farmaya : Ata ke ilawa deegar muhaddesin ne farmaya : wo (jinki baari muqarrar nahin thi) Sauda (Raziallahu anha) thin, aur yehi baat zyada sahih hai, kyonkey jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen Talaq deney ka irada farmaya to unhoney apni baari Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko hiba kar di thi, aur unhoney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kya : maine apni baari Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko hiba kar di, taake main jannat mein aap ki paak biviyon mein se hun."
3238,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aurton ke sath khair w bhalai se pesh aao, kyonkey wo pasli se paida ki gaee hain, aur pasli ka ooper wala hissey sab se ziyada tedha hota hai, agar tum usey sidha karney ki koshish karogey to usey tod betho gey, aur agar usey chhod dogey to wo tedha rahega, tum aurton ke sath khair w bhalai ka khayal rakho.'' muttafaq aleh."
3239,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aurat pasli se paida ki gaee hai, wo aap ke sath kabhi eik andaz par guzar basar nahin karegi, agar tum us se faeyda hasil karna chahtey ho to tum uskey tedhey pan ke sath hi us se faeyda hasil karo, aur agar tum ne usey sidha karney ki koshish ki to tum usey tod dogey , aur usey todna usey Talaq dena hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
3240,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi momin ( shohar ( kisi momina ( biwi ( se bughz na rakhey, agar uski koi eik aadat usey napasand hai to koi dusri aadat pasand bhi hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3241,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bani-Israel na hotey to gosht kharab na hota aur agar Hawa na hotin to koi aurat kabhi apney shohar ki khayanat na karti.'' muttafaq aleh."
3242,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Zam-aa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi apni biwi ko ghulam ki tarah na maarey aur phir wo din ke aakhir pahar us se mujaamiat karey.'' aur dusri riwayat mein hai : ''tum mein se koi qasd (irada) karta hai to apni aurat ko ghulam ki tarah maarta hai, aur phir mumkin hai ke wo usi roz aakhiri pahar us se mujaamiat karey.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen gooz maarney ( reeh ki aawaz ( par hansney ke mutalliq nasihat ki to farmaya : ''tum mein se koi aisi chiz par kyon hansta hai jo wo khud karta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3243,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan gudiyon ke sath khela karti thi, aur meri kuch saheliyaan thin jo merey sath kheltii thin, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif latey to wo aap se chup jatin , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhen meri taraf bhejtey to phir wo merey sath kheltin. muttafaq aleh."
3244,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Allah ki qism ! maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko apney hujrey ke darwazey par khadey huey dekha jabkey Habshi masjid mein chhotey nezon ke sath khel rahey they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni chadar se mujhey chupa rahey they taake main aap ke kaan aur gardan ke bech se unke khel ko dekh sakun, phir aap meri khatir khadey rehtey yahan tak ke main hi wahan se hati thi, tum no-umr, khel se dilchaspi rakhney wali, ladki ke khadey honey ka andaza kar lo. (ke wo kitni der khadi ho sakti hai. ( muttafaq aleh."
3245,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''jab tum mujh se razi hoti ho to mujhey pata chal jata hai aur isi tarah jab tum mujh se naraz hoti ho to tab bhi mujhey pata chal jata hai.'' maine arz kya : aap ye kaisey pehchantey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mujh se razi hoti ho to tum kehti ho : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke rab ki qasam! aur jab tum mujh se naraz hoti ho to tum kehti ho : Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ke rab ki qasam! Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain : maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! Allah ki qism ! bilkul theek hai, main sirf aap ka naam hi chhodti hun. muttafaq aleh."
3246,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi apni ehliya ko apney bistar par bulaey aur wo inkar kar dey aur wo (khaawind) narazi mein so jaey to subh honey tak farishtey us ( aurat ( par lanat bhejtey rehtey hain.'' Bukhari, Muslim. aur saheehain ki hi riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai! jab koi aadmi apni ehliya ko apney bistar par bulaey aur wo is par inkar kar dey to aasman wali zaat ( Allah Taala (us par naraz ho jati hai yahan tak ke wo ( khawind (us se razi ho jaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
3247,"Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aurat ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! meri eik sautan hai, to kya mujh par gunah hoga ke main apney khawind ki taraf se kisi aisi chiz ka izhar karun jo usney mujhey na di ho? (taake meri sautan tang ho) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aisi chiz zahir karney wala jo usey na di gaee ho jhoot ka joda zeb tan karney waley (yani dhokey baaz) ki tarah hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3248,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni paak biviyon se eik maah elaa farmaya. aap ke paaon mein moch aa gaee thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne untees raaten baalaakhaane mein qiyam farmaya phir aap nichey tashrif ley aaye to Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! aapney eik maah ke liye qism uthai thi ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mahina untees ka bhi hota hai.'' Bukhari ."
3249,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir honey ke liye ijazat talab karna chahi to unhoney logon ko darwazey par bethey huey paya jin mein se kisi ko ijazat na mili thi, raawi bayan kartey hain : abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko ijazat mil gaee to wo andar chaley gaey, phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) aaye , unhoney ijazat talab ki to unhen bhi ijazat mil gaee , unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko pareshani ke aalim mein khamosh betha hua paya jabkey aap ki paak biviyan aap ke ird-gird thin . raawi bayan kartey hain : unhon (yani umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : main koi aisi baat kahunga jis se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko hansaaunga. unhoney kaha : Allah ke Rasool ! agar khaarija ki beti mujh se kharcha maangti to main uski gardan marod deta , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) muskura diye aur farmaya : '' unhoney merey gird ghera dal rakha hai, jaisa ke tum dekh rahey ho, aur mujh se kharcha mang rahi hain.'' ( ye sun kar) abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) , Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf badhey aur unki sarzanish ki, aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) , Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ki gardan kootney lagey , aur wo dono keh rahey they : tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se aisi chiz ka mutalba karti ho, jo unke paas nahin hai, unhoney kaha : Allah ki qism ! ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kabhi aisi chiz ka mutalba nahin kerengi jo aap ke paas na ho, phir aap eik maah ya untees din un se alag rahey, aur phir ye aayat nazil hui : ''aey Nabi ! apni azwaj (jodey) se farmaain . . . . . . tum mein se mohsanaat ke liye bada ajr hai.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se ibtida (shuruat) farmaai to farmaya : '' Aaisha ! main tumharey samney eik baat pesh karna chahta hun, aur main pasand karta hun ke tujhey is barey mein jald bazi nahin kerni chahiye jab tak tum apney waliden se mashwara na kar lo .'' unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! wo kya baat hai? aapney unhen wo aayat sunai to unhoney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya main aap ke barey mein apney waliden se mashwara karungi, nahin, balke main Allah, uskey Rasool aur daare-aakhirat ko ikhtiyar karti hun, aur main aap se mutalba karti hun ke maine aap se jo baat ki hai wo aap apni paak biviyon mein se kisi eik ko mat bataeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mujh se to jo bhi puchegi mein usey zarur bataaunga , kyonkey Allah ne mujhey ( logon ko) ranj w mashaqqat mein mubtala karney ke liye nahin bheja balke usney mujhey aasani paida karney wala muallim bana kar bheja hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
3250,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, main un aurton ki mazammat kya karti thi jinhon ne apney aap ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye hiba kya tha, maine kaha : kya aurat apney aap ko hiba kar sakti hai? jab Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaai : ''aap un mein se jisey chahen door karen aur jisey chahen apni taraf thikana den aur jinko alag kya unmein se jisey chahen talab farmaain to aap par koi gunah nahin.'' to maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kya : main aapke rab ko dekhti hun ke wo aapki khaahish ko jald pura karta hai. muttafaq aleh. ( وَ حَدِیْثُ jaabir : ( اِتَّقُوا اللہَ فِی النِّسَاءِ ( ذُکِرَ فِیْ قِصَّۃِ حَجَّۃِ الْوَدَاع .) aur Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees '' aurton ke maamle mein Allah se daro '' Hajjatil-wadaa ke qissa mein zikr ki gaee hai."
3251,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke wo eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath thin, wo bayan karti hain, maine aap se muqabla kya to main daud mein aap se aagey badh gaee , jab main farba ho gaee to maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se muqabla kya, tab aap mujh se aagey nikal gaey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye us pehel ka badla ho gaya .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3252,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se behtar wo hai jo apney ghar walon ke liye behtar hai, aur main apney ghar walon ke liye tum sab se behtar hun, aur jab tumhara koi sathi faut ho jaey to usey chhod do (uski buraaiyan bayan na karo) .'' rawahu Tirmizi w Darmi."
3253,Hazrat ibne-Maja ne ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se ( لَاھْلِیْ ( tak riwayat kya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja .
3254,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aurat paanchon namazein padhey, maah Ramazan ke rozey rakhey, apni sharm-gah ki hifazat karey aur apney khawind ki itaat karey to phir wo jannat ke jis darwazey se chahey dakhil ho jaey.'' (rawahu abu-Nuem) ."
3255,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar main kisi ko hukm deta ke wo kisi shakhs ko (bator tazeem) sajda karey to main aurat ko hukm deta ke wo apney shohar ko sajda karey.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
3256,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo aurat us haal mein faut ho ke uska shohar us se razi ho to wo jannat mein dakhil hogi.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
3257,"Hazrat Talaq bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi apni ehliya ko apni hajat ke liye bulaey to usey uskey paas jana chahiye chahey wo tanur par ho.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
3258,"Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' koi aurat apney shohar ko duniya mein takleef pahunchati hai to uski badi badi aakhon wali jannati biwi kehti hai : Allah tujhey halak karey, usey takleef na pahuncha , wo to terey paas bas mehman hai, wo an-qareeb tujhey chhod kar hamari taraf chala aaeyga .'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
3259,"Hazrat Hakim bin Muawiya Qusheri apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! biwi ka khawind par kya haq hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum khaao to usey bhi khilao, jab tum pahno to usey bhi pehnao, uskey chehrey par na maaro, na usey bura-bhala kaho aur) narazi par) sirf ghar mein us se alehdgi ikhtiyar karo.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
3260,"Hazrat Laqeet bin Sabra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! meri eik biwi hai uski zaban mein kuch ( naqs ( hai yani wo fohsh bhale hi hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey Talaq dey do .'' maine arz kya, meri us se aulad hai aur uskey sath eik talluq hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey waaz w nasihat karo, agar is mein koi khair w bhalai hui to wo nasihat qubul kar legi, aur apni ehliya ko londi ki tarah na maaro .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3261,"Hazrat Ayas bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki laundiyon ( apni biwiyon ( ko na maaro .'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya : aurten apney khaawindon par jurat karney lagi hain, tab aapney unhen maarney ke mutalliq rukhsat ata farmaai to bahut si aurten Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki paak biviyon ke paas apney khaawindon ki shikayat lekar ayen to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' bahut si aurten apney khaawindon ki shikayat lekar Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki biviyon ke paas aain hain, aisey log (jo apni azwaj (jodey) ko maartay hain ( tum mein se behtar nahin hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
3262,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi aurat ko uskey khawind ke khilaf ya ghulam ko uskey aaqa ke khilaf bhadkaaye wo ham mein se nahin .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3263,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mominon mein se kamil eman wala shakhs wo hai jo un mein se achey akhlaq wala aur apney ghar walon ke sath ziyada meharban hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
3264,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mominon mein se kamil eman wala wo shakhs hai jo in mein se achey akhlaq wala hai, aur tum mein se behtar wo hai jo apni aurton ke liye behtar hai.'' Tirmizi . aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. aur Imam Abu-Dawood ne usey ( خُلُقًا ( tak riwayat kya hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
3265,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghazwa tabuk ya ghazwa Hunain se wapis tashrif laye, aur un ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ( ki almari par parda tha, hawa chali to usney Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki gudiyon aur khilonon se parda hata diya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Aaisha ! ye kya hai? '' unhoney arz kya : meri gudiyaan hain, aapney un main eik ghoda dekha jiskey kapdey se baney huey do par they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main unke darmiyan mein ye kya dekh raha hun ?'' unhoney arz kya : ghoda hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aur jo is ke ooper hai, wo kya hai? '' unhoney arz kya : do par hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ghoda aur uskey do par! '' unhoney arz kya : kya aapney nahin suna ke Suleman (Alaihissalam) (Alaihissalam) ka eik ghoda tha jiskey par they.'' wo bayan karti hain, ye sun kar aap muskura diye yahan tak ke maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki daadhein dekhin. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3266,"Hazrat Qais bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Hera pahuncha to maine wahan ke bashindon ko apney sipeh saalaar ko sajda kartey huey dekha to maine kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka ziyada haq hai ke unhen sajda kya jaey. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to arz kya : main Hera gaya tha maine wahan ke bashindon ko apney sipeh-saalaar ko sajda kartey huey dekha, aap ziyada haqdaar hain ke aap ko sajda kya jaey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey bataao agar tum meri qabr ke paas se guzro to kya tum usey sajda karogey?'' maine arz kya, nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mat karo, agar main kisi ko hukm deta ke wo kisi ko sajda karey to main aurton ko hukm deta ke wo apney khaawindon ko sajda karen isliye ke Allah ne unhen un par haq ata kya hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3267,Hazrat Imam Ahmed ne usey Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu Ahmed .
3268,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khaawind se daryaft na kya jaey ke usney apni biwi ko kyon maara hai? '' rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
3269,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke eik aurat aap ke paas aai to usney arz kya : mera khawind Safwan bin muattal, jab main Namaz padhti hun to wo mujhey maarta hai, jab main ( nafli ( roza rakhti hun to wo mujhey iftaar karney ka hukm deta hai, aur wo Suraj tulu honey par namaze-Fajr padhta hai. raawi bayan kartey hain, Safwan aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas hi tha, raawi ne kaha : aapney us chiz ke mutalliq jo us (aurat) ne kaha tha Safwan se daryaft kya, to usney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! raha uska ye kehna ke jab main Namaz padhti hun to wo mujhey maarta hai, uski wajeh ye hai ke ye do suraten padhti hai. halanke maine usey mana kya hai, raawi bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Safwan se farmaya : ''agar eik hi sura hoti wo logon ke liye kafi hoti. Safwan ne kaha : raha uska ye kehna ke jab main roza rakhti hun to wo mujhey iftaar kara deta hai. to uski wajeh ye hai ke ye rozey rakhti chali jati hai jabkey main nojawan aadmi hun, main (jimaa sey) ruk nahin sakta, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aurat apney khawind ki ijazat ke baghair (nafli) rozey na rakhey .'' aur uska ye kehna ke main Suraj tulu honey par Namaz padhta hun, uski wajeh ye hai ke hamarey gharaney ke mutalliq mashhoor hai ke ham Suraj tulu honey par hi bedaar hotey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Safwan! jab tum bedaar ho tab Namaz padh liya karo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja."
3270,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) muhajrin w ansaar ki jamaat mein they ke itney main eik oont aaya aur usney aap ko sajda kya. aapke Sahaba ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! chopaey aur darkht aapko sajda kartey hain, jabkey ham to ziyada haqdaar mein ke ham aap ko sajda karen, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney rab ki ibadat karo aur apney bhai ki izzat karo, agar main kisi ko hukm karta ke wo kisi ko sajda karey to main aurat ko hukm deta ke wo apney khawind ko sajda karey, aur agar wo usey hukm dey ke wo Jabal Asfar ( zard pahad ( se Jabal Aswad ( kalay pahad ( ki taraf aur Jabal Aswad ko Jabal Abyaz ki taraf pathar muntaqil kar dey to usey chahiye ke wo aisa hi karey.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
3271,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen qism ke log aisey hain jinki na Namaz qubul hoti hai aur na koi neki ooper chadhti hai : farar hua ghulam yahan tak ke wo apney malikon ke paas wapis aa jaey aur apna haath unke haath mein de-dey, wo aurat jis par uska khawind naraz ho, aur nashey wala yahan tak ke wo hosh mein aa jaey.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
3272,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya : kon si aurat behtar hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo jo apney khawind ko khush kar dey jab wo usey dekhey, aur jab usey hukm dey to wo uski itaat karey aur apney maal w jaan mein khawind ki marzi ke khilaf aisa kaam na karey jo usey napasand ho.'' , ( rawahu Nasai w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
3273,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chaar chizen aisi hain jisey mil jaeyn to usey duniya w aakhirat ki bhalai mil gaee, shukr guzar dil, zikr karney wali zaban, takleefon mein sabr karney wala badan aur aisi aurat jo apney khawind se apni zaat ke barey mein aur uskey maal ke barey mein khayanat ki Talib na ho.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
3274,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Sabit bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui to usney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! mujhey Sabit bin Qais ki aadatein aur Deendari par koi aetraz nahin lekin main Islam mein (khaawind ki) nafarmani ko napasand karti hun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum uska baagh wapis kar dogi?'' usney arz kya : ji haan! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sabit ko kaha : ''baagh qubul karo aur usey eik Talaq de-do.'' Bukhari ."
3275,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney apni biwi ko haiz key dinon mein Talaq di. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne uskey mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se zikr kya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is par naraz huye, aur farmaya : ''usey chahiye ke wo ruju karey, phir intizar karey yahan tak ke wo (haiz key din guzarney ke baad) paak ho jaey, phir haiz aaye, phir paak ho, phir agar usey Talaq dena chahey to usey haalate-tuhur mein jima karney se pehley Talaq dey, yehi wo iddat hai jiskey mutabiq Allah ne aurton ko Talaq deney ka hukm farmaya hai.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''usey hukm do ke wo ruju karey, phir usey haalate-tuhur ya hamal mein Talaq dey.'' muttafaq aleh."
3276,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen ikhtiyar diya to ham ne Allah aur uskey Rasool ko muntakhab kya, aapney usey hamarey mutalliq kuch bhi shumar na kya. muttafaq aleh."
3277,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kisi chiz ko haram qarar deney par kaffara ada karney ka zikr kartey huey farmaya : ''tumharey liye Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ki zindagi) mein behtareen namoona hai.'' muttafaq aleh.
3278,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zenab binte Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan thehra kartey they aur wahan shehad piya kartey they, pas main aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne tey kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jiskey paas bhi tashrif laeyn to wo kahey : mujhey aap se maghafeer (khaney ka gond jo arfat paudey se nikalta hai) ki boo aa rahi hai, kya aapney maghaafeer khaya hai? chunanche aap un dono mein se kisi eik ke yahan tashrif ley gaey to usney aap se yehi kaha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aisi koi baat nahin, maine to Zenab ke yahan shehad piya hai, main dobara usey nahin piyunga, aur maine halaf utha liya, tum kisi ko uskey mutalliq na batana.'' aap apni azwaj (jodey) ki raza-mandi chahtey they chunanche ye aayat nazil hui : ''aey Nabi aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us chiz ko kyon haram qarar diya jisey Allah ne aapke liye halal qarar diya hai, aap apni azwaj (jodey) ki raza-mandi chahtey hain ?'' muttafaq aleh."
3279,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo aurat bila wajeh apney khawind se Talaq ka mutalba karey to is par jannat ki khushbu haram hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja w Darmi."
3280,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''halal chizon mein se Allah ke nazdik sab se ziyada naa-pasandida chiz Talaq hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood .
3281,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nikah se pehley Talaq deney , milkiyat se pehley azad karney , musalsal rozey rakhney, baligh honey ke baad yateem, doodh chudaney ke baad doodh pilaney aur subh se raat tak khamoshi ikhtiyar karney ka koi jawaz nahin.'' ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
3282,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''insan jis chiz ka Malik nahin, is mein uska nazar dena, azad karna aur Talaq dena moatabar nahin hai.'' aur Abu-Dawood ne ye alfaz ziyada kiye hain : ''insan jis chiz ka Malik hai usi ka sauda kar sakta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
3283,"Hazrat Rukana bin Abd Yazid se riwayat hai ke unhoney apni ehliya Suhema ko Talaq bitta di, unhoney uskey mutalliq Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya aur kaha : Allah ki qism ! maine sirf eik hi ka irada kya tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne sirf eik hi ka irada kya tha ?'' Rukana ne arz kya : Allah ki qism ! maine eik hi ka irada kya tha.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Suhaima ko Rukana ki taraf lota diya, phir unhoney dusri Talaq umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke doore-hukoomat mein aur teesri Talaq Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke doore-hukoomat mein di. Abu-Dawood. aur Tirmizi, ibne-Maja, Darmi, magar unhoney dusri aur teesri Talaq ka zikr nahin kya. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
3284,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen chizen haqiqat mein bhi haqiqat hain aur mazaaq mein bhi haqiqat hain : Nikah, Talaq aur Ruju.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
3285,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' jabr ki surat mein na Talaq moatabar hai aur na azad karna.'' aur '' aghlaaq '' ka maana '' jabr '' hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
3286,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''majnun aur maghloobul-aql ki Talaq ke siwa her Talaq waqey ho jati hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. aur Ata bin Ajlan raawi zaeef hai, wo hadees yad rakhney wala nahin. rawahu Tirmizi ."
3287,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teen shakhs par koi saza nahi hain, soyaa hua yahan tak ke jaag jaey, bachcha yahan tak ke baligh ho jaey, aur majnun yahan tak ke wo hosh mand ho jaey.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
3288,Darmi ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se aur ibne-Maja ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu Darmi w ibne-Maja .
3289,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' londi ki Talaq do talaaqein hain aur uski iddat do haiz hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja w Darmi .
3290,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nafarmani karney waliyan aur Khula talab karney waliyan munafiq hain.'' rawahu Nasai .
3291,"Hazrat Naafe, Safiya binte-abi Ubaid ki azad karda londi se riwayat kartey hain ke usney apni her chiz ke badley apney khawind ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se Khula liya to Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne uska inkar na kya. rawahu Malik."
3292,"Hazrat Mehmood bin labid bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik aadmi ke mutalliq bataya gaya ke usney apni biwi ko teen talaaqein eik sath de-di hain, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghussa ki haalat mein khadey huey phir farmaya : ''kya Allah azz-w-jall ki kitab se khela ja raha hai jabkey main tumharey darmiyan mojud hun.'' is par eik aadmi khada hua aur usney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya main usey qatl na kar dun? rawahu Nasai."
3293,"Hazrat Imam Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhen ye baat pahunchi ke eik aadmi ne Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : maine apni biwi ko so talaaqein di hain, aap ki is barey mein kya raey hai? ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ''usey teri taraf se teen talaaqein to waqey ho gaeen, jabkey sattaanwey ke zariey tum ne Allah ki aayaat ke sath mazaq kya. rawahu Malik."
3294,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey hukm farmaya : ''Muaz! Allah ne roey-zameen par jo kuch paida farmaya hai is mein kisi ( ghulam ( ko azad karna usey sab se ziyada mehbub hai, aur usney roey zamin par jo kuch paida farmaya hai is mein se Talaq usey intehai napasand hai.'' rawahu Dar-Qutni ."
3295,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rifaa Qarzi ki biwi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui to usney arz kya : main Rifaa ke nikah mein thi to usney mujhey teen talaaqein de-din. uskey baad maine Abdur-Rehman bin Zuber se shaadi kar li, lekin uskey paas to kapdey ke pallu ki tarah hai (yani wo jima ke qabil nahin) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum Rifaa ki taraf wapis jana chahti ho?'' usney arz kya : ji haan, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, yahan tak ke tum us se lutf andoz ho jaao aur wo tum se lutf andoz ho jaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
3296,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Halala karney waley aur jis ke liye Halala kya ja raha hai dono par lanat farmaai. rawahu Darmi ."
3297,"Hazrat ibne-Maja ne isey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) , ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja ."
3298,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke taqriban das Sahaba se mulaqat ki wo sab kehtey they ke elaa karney waley ko pabande-salaasil kya jaeyga. (Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
3299,"Hazrat abu-Salma se riwayat hai ke Salman bin Sakhr , unhen Salma bin Sakhr bayazi bhi kaha jata hai, ne apni biwi ko pura Ramazan apney ooper apni maa ki pusht ki tarah qarar dey liya , jab nisf Ramazan guzar gaya to eik raat usney us se jima kar liya , phir wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur uskey mutalliq aap se zikr kya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : '' eik ghulam azad karo.'' usney arz kya, merey paas koi ghulam nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' do maah ke musalsal rozey rakho .'' usney arz kya : main istataat nahin rakhta , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' saath miskinon ko khana khilao.'' usney arz kya : main taqat nahin rakhta , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farwa bin Amr se farmaya : ''usey pandarah saa ya sola ( taqriban chaalis kilo) wala khajuron ka tokraa dey do taake wo saath miskinon ko khila dey .'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
3300,"Hazrat Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja aur Darmi ne Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yasar ke tareeq se Salma bin Sakhr se isi tarah riwayat kya hai, unhoney kaha : mujhey jis qadr aurton se lagaao tha itna lagaao merey siwa kisi ko na tha. aur un dono yani Abu-Dawood aur Darmi ki riwayat mein hai : '' eik wasq ( saath saa ( khajuren saath miskinon ko khilao.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
3301,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yasar , Salma bin sakhr ki sanad se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey, zihar karney waley ke mutalliq jo kaffara deney se pehley jima kar ley, riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' eik hi kaffara hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
3302,"Hazrat Ikrima, ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke eik aadmi ne apni biwi se zihar kya to usney kaffara ada karney se pehley us se jima kar liya, phir wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney uskey mutalliq aap ko bataya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumhen kis chiz ne is par aamada kya ?'' usney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! maine chaandni raat mein uski paazeb ki safedi dekhi to mujh se raha na gaya aur main us se ham bistar ho gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) muskura diye aur usey hukm farmaya ke wo kaffara ada karney se pehley uskey qarib na jaey. ibne-Maja. aur Imam Tirmizi ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya hai, aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. aur Imam Abu-Dawood aur Imam Nasai ne isi ki tarah musnad aur mursal riwayat kya hai, aur Imam Nasai ne farmaya : mursal durust honey mein , musnad se behtar hai. rawahu ibne-Maja w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
3303,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Hakam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! meri eik londi meri bakriyan charaati thi, main uskey paas aaya to maine eik bakri na pai, maine uskey mutalliq us se puchha to usney kaha : usey bhediye ne kha liya hai, main us se naraz hua , chunkey main aulade-Adam se hun, maine uskey chehrey par thappad maar diya, (aur kisi wajeh sey) ghulam azad karna mujh par wajib hai, kya main usey azad kar dun? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us londi se puchha : ''Allah kahan hai? '' usney kaha : aasman mein , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main kon hun ?'' usney arz kya, aap Allah ke Rasool hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey azad kar do .'' ye Malik ki riwayat hai, aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : unhon ( Muawiya bin Hakam (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : meri eik londi thi jo Uhud aur jawwaaniya ki taraf meri bakriyan charaaya karti thi, eik roz maine dekha ke bhediya hamari bakriyon mein se eik bakri ley gaya, chunkey mein Adam ki aulad se hun, main bhi naraz hota hun jaisey wo naraz hotey hain, isliye maine usey eik thappad maar diya phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua (aur sara waqia sunaya ( aapney meri is harkat ko bada jurm qarar diya, maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya main usey azad na kar dun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey merey paas laao.'' main usey aap ke paas ley aaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se puchha : ''Allah kahan hai?'' usney arz kya : aasman mein , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main kon hun ?'' usney kaha : aap Allah ke Rasool hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey azad kar do kyonkey ye musalman hai.'' rawahu Malik w Muslim ."
3304,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Uwemir Ajlaani ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! us shakhs ke barey mein bataeyn jo apni biwi ke sath kisi mard ko paey, kya wo usey qatl kar dey, is surat mein wo (maqtool ke warison) usko qatl kar dengey ya usey kya karna chahiye? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' terey aur teri biwi ke barey mein hukm nazil ho chuka hai, tum usey lekar aao.'' Sehal bayan kartey hain, un dono ne masjid mein liaan kya, aur main logon ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas tha, jab wo dono farigh huey to Uwemir ne kaha : Allah ke Rasool! agar main usey rakh lun to uska matlab hoga maine is par jhoot baandha, usney usey teen talaaqein de-din, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' intizar karo aur dekho agar wo siyah rang , moti moti aur khub siyah aakhon waley, peeth badey badey aur moti moti pindliyon waley bachey ko janm dey to phir main samjhunga ke Uwemir ne uskey mutalliq sach kaha hai, aur agar wo surkh rang ka hua, goya ke wo zehreeli chhipkali hai to main samjhunga ke Uwemir ne us aurat par jhoot baandha hai.'' us aurat ne is tarah ke bachey ko janm diya jis tarah ki sifaat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Uwemir ki tasdeeq ke mutalliq bayan farmaai thin, uskey baad us bachey ko uski maa ki taraf mansub kya jata tha. muttafaq aleh."
3305,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne shohar aur uski biwi ke darmiyan liaan karaya, us ( aadmi ( ne uskey bachey ko qubul karney se inkar kar diya to aapney un dono ke darmiyan tafriq kara di aur bachey ko aurat ke hawaley kar diya. aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki saheehain ki hadees mein hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne pehley shohar ko waaz w nasihat ki aur usey bataya ke duniya ka azab aakhirat ke azab se bahut halka hai, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us aurat ko bulaya aur usey bhi waaz w nasihat ki aur usey bhi bataya ke duniya ka azab aakhirat ke azab se bahut halka hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3306,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne liaan karney walon se farmaya : ''tumhara hisab Allah ke zimme hai, tum dono mein se eik jhoota hai, ab tumhara us ( aurat ( par koi haq nahin.'' us ( aadmi ( ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! mera maal ( jo mehar mein diya tha ( ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumhen maal ka koi haq nahin, agar tum ne uskey mutalliq sachi baat ki hai to wo ( maal ( uska badal hai jo tum ne us se ham-bistari ki hai, aur agar tum ne uskey mutalliq jhooti baat ki hai to phir us ( mehar (ka lotna tumharey liye baeed hai aur tera us se mutalba karna bhi baeed hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3307,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hilal bin Umayya ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas apni biwi par shareek bin Sehma ke sath zina ki tohmat lagai to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''subut pesh karo, warna teri pusht par had qaaim hogi .'' usney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! jab ham mein se koi apni biwi ko haalate-zina mein dekhey to kya wo gawah talash karney chala jaey ? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' gawah pesh karo warna tumhari pusht par had qaaim ki jaeygi .'' Hilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya is zaat ki qism jisney aap ko haq ke sath Nabi banakar bheja hai ! main yaqinan sacha hun Allah aisa hukm zarur nazil farmaeyga jo mujhey had se bacha lega . pas Jibrael (Alaihissalam) tashrif laye aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par ye aayaat nazil farmaain : ''jo log apni biwiyon par tohmat lagatey hain. . . . . . . . . agar wo sahon mein se hai.'' Hilal aaye to unhoney gawahi di (yani liaan kya ( jabkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma rahey they : '' yaqinan tum mein se eik jhoota hai to kya wo tauba karney ke liye tayyar hai? '' phir aurat khadi hui to usney gawahi di ( liaan kya ( jab wo paanchwen gawahi par pahunchi to unhoney usey roka aur unhoney kaha ke ye ( paanchwin gawahi ( wajib karney wali hai? ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : usney twaqquf kya aur khamoshi ikhtiyar ki yahan tak ke ham ne samjha ke wo (apney mauqif sey) ruju kar legi , phir usney kaha : main hamesha ke liye apni qom ko ruswa nahin karungi. chunanche usney paanchwin gawahi bhi de-di to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey dekho agar ye surmai aakhon waley, badey peeth waley aur moti pindliyon waley bachey ko janm dey to phir wo shareek bin Sehma ka hai.'' usney isi tarah ke bachey ko janm diya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar Allah ka hukm (ke liaan ke baad had jari nahin ki jaeygi ( pehley se na aaya hota to main usey zarur saza deta.'' Bukhari ."
3308,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya agar main kisi aadmi ko apni biwi ke sath qabile-aetraz haalat mein paaun to kya main us (aadmi) ko haath na lagaaun yahan tak ke main chaar gawah laaun? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan!'' unhoney arz kya, hergiz nahin, us zaat ki qism jisney aap ko haq ke sath Nabi banakar bheja! agar merey sath aisa hua to main us ( gawahi ( se pehley hi talwaar ke zariey uska kaam tamam kar dunga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apney sardar ki baat ghor se suno , kyonkey wo ghayyur shakhs hai, aur main us se ziyada ghayyur hun jabkey Allah mujh se ziyada ghayyur hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
3309,"Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : agar main apni biwi ke sath kisi aadmi ko) haalate-zina mein) dekh lun to main talwaar ki dhaar ke sath usey qatl kar dun. ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tak pahunchi to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum Saad ki ghairat se tajjub kartey ho? Allah ki qism ! main us se ziyada ghairat mand hun aur Allah mujh se ziyada ghairat mand hai, aur Allah ne apni ghairat hi ke baais zahiri aur batni be hayai ko haram qarar diya hai, aur Allah se ziyada koi shakhs uzr-pasand nahin karta isi liye to usney aagah karney waley aur khushkhabri sunaney waley (anbiya (Alaihissalam)) maboos farmaey, aur Allah se badh kar koi shakhs madah ko pasand nahin karta, usi liye to Allah ne jannat ka wada kya hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3310,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala ghairatmand hai aur be-shak momin bhi ghairat mand hai, aur Allah ki ghairat ye hai ke momin Allah ki haram ki hui chiz ka irtikab na karey.'' muttafaq aleh."
3311,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik Erabi (dehati) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kya : meri biwi ne eik siyah bachey ko janm diya hai, maine usey qubul karney se inkar kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya terey paas kuch oont hain?'' usney arz kya : haan, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unke rang kaisey hain?'' usney arz kya : surkh, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya in mein koi khaaki rang ka bhi hai? '' usney arz kya : un mein khaaki rang ka bhi hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumharey khayal mein ye kahan se aa gaya?'' usney arz kya : ( purani ( rag usey ley aai hogi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mumkin hai ye bhi rag ho jo usey ley aai ho.'' aur aapney usey us bachey se inkar ki ijazat nahin di. muttafaq aleh."
3312,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Utba bin abi Waqas ne apney bhai Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ko wasiyat ki ke Zam-aa ki londi ka ladka mera hai. tum usey apney qabzey mein le-lena . chunanche jab Fateh Makka ka saal hua to Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey ley liya aur kaha : ye mera bhatija hai. aur abd bin Zam-aa ne kaha : ye mera bhai hai, wo dono Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey . Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! merey bhai ne us ( bachey (ke barey mein mujhey wasiyat ki thi, aur abd bin Zam-aa ne arz kya, ye mera bhai hai aur merey walid ki londi ka beta hai uskey bistar par paida hua hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' abd bin Zam-aa bacha tumhen milega kyonkey bacha usi ka hota hai jiskey bistar par paida hua ho, jabkey zaani ke liye pathar (yani rajm) hai.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sauda binte-Zam-aa (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''us se parda kya karo.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye tab farmaya jab aapney us ladkey ki Utba se mushaabihat dekhi. uskey baad usney Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ko zindagi bhar nahin dekha. aur eik riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' abd bin Zam-aa ! wo tumhara bhai hai, isliye ke wo uskey walid ke bistar par paida hua hai. muttafaq aleh."
3313,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, eik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) badey khush khush merey paas tashrif laye aur farmaya : '' Aaisha kya tujhey malum nahin ke Mujazziz Mudliji aaya hua hai jab usney Usama aur Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko us haal mein dekha ke un dono par eik chadar thi aur unhoney apney saron ko us se dhanp rakha tha aur unke paaon nangey they, usney kaha : ye paaon eik doosrey se hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
3314,"Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) aur abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne jantey-boojhtey apney aap ko apney baap ke ilawa kisi aur ki taraf mansub kya to aisey shakhs par jannat haram hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3315,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apney aaba se be raghbati w aeraz na karo, kyonkey jis shakhs ne apney baap se aeraz kya (aur apney aap ko kisi aur ki taraf mansub kya) usney kufr kya. ''muttafaq aleh. ( وَقَدْ ذُکِرَ حَدِیْثُ عَائِشَۃَ (Raziallahu anhu)) maa مِنْ اَحَدٍ اَغْیَرُ مِنَ اللہِ ( فِیْ بَابِ صَلْوۃِ الْخُسُوْفِ .) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''Allah se badh kar koi ghairat mand nahin .'' ( salaat الخسوف (ke baab mein zikr ki gaee hai"
3316,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab liaan ke mutalliq aayat nazil hui to unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo aurat bachey ko aisi qom mein dakhil kar dey jisse unka naata nahin Allah ke nazdik us aurat ki koi izzat nahin aur wo usey jannat mein dakhil nahin farmaeyga, aur jo shakhs apney bachey ka inkar kar dey halanke usey malum hai ke ye bacha usi ka hai, Allah us se hijaab farma lega aur usko tamam awwal w aakhir puri makhluq ke samney ruswa kar dega.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai w Darmi ."
3317,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney arz kya : meri biwi hai jo kisi chhuney waley ka haath nahin rokti , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey Talaq dey do .'' usney arz kya : main us se mohabbat karta hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' phir usey apney nikah mein rakh .'' aur Imam Nasai (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : kisi raawi ne usey ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se marfoo naqal kya hai aur kisi ne marfooan zikr nahin kya. chunanche Imam Nasai kehtey hain ye hadees Sabit nahin. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
3318,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se naqal kartey hain ke Nabi mukarram (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us bachey ki baabat faisla sadir farmaya jisey uskey baap ke marney ke baad uskey warison mein shamil kya gaya ho. agar wo bacha aisi londi ka hai ke marney waley shakhs ne us londi se us waqt ham-bistari ki thi jab wo us londi ka Malik tha to wo bacha uskey warison mein shamil hai uskey paida honey se pehley jo virasat taqseem ho chuki us se wo mehroom rahega albatta paida honey ke waqt jo tarka mojud tha is mein se usey hissey milega (jis bachey ko shamil kya ja raha hai) agar uskey walid ne marney se qabl usey qubul karney se inkar kar diya tha to phir us bachey ko warison mein shamil nahin kya jaeyga, agar wo bacha aisi londi se hai jis ka wo mutwaffii (marnewla) Malik nahin tha ya wo aisi azad aurat se jo uskey nikah mein na thi to us bachey ko mutwaffii ke nasab mein shamil nahin kya jaeyga lihaza wo bacha mutwaffii ka waris nahin banega , agar-che us bachey ko khud mutwaffii ne apna beta hi kyon na qarar diya ho kyonkey wo zina ki pedawar hai chahey londi se ho ya azad aurat se ho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3319,"Hazrat Jabir bin Ateek (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghairat ki eik qism aisi hai jisey Allah pasand karta hai aur eik qism aisi hai jisey Allah pasand nahin farmata, rahi wo jisey Allah pasand farmata hai, wo hai jo maqam shak mein ho, aur rahi wo jisey Allah napasand farmata hai wo ghairat hai jo ghair shak ( guman ( mein ho. aur fakhr ki eik aisi qism hai jisey Allah napasand karta hai, aur eik aisi qism hai jisey Allah pasand farmata hai raha wo fakhr jisey Allah pasand farmata hai wo aadmi ka qitaal ( jihad (aur sadqa ke waqt fakhr karna hai, aur raha wo jisey Allah napasand farmata hai to wo nasab mein fakhr karna hai.'' aur dusri riwayat mein hai : '' zulm mein fakhr karna.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
3320,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke eik aadmi khada hua aur usney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! falan mera beta hai, maine daure-jahiliyat mein uski maa se zina kya tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Islam mein) bachey ka ( dawa nahin, jahiliyat ka maamla khatam ho gaya, bacha sahibe-bistar ke liye hai aur zaani ke liye pathar ( rajm (sangsar) ya mehroomi) hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3321,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chaar qisam ki aurton ke darmiyan koi liaan nahin, nasrani aurat musalman ke nikah mein ho, Yahudi aurat musalman ke nikah mein ho, azad aurat mamlook ke nikah mein ho, aur mamlook aurat azad ke nikah mein ho.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
3322,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko us waqt hukm farmaya , jab aapney do liaan karney walon ko liaan karney ka hukm diya tha ke wo (aadmi) paanchwen shahadat ke waqt us (liaan karney waley) ke munh par haath rakh dey , aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kyonkey wo (paanchwen gawahi) wajib karney wali hai.'' rawahu Nasai."
3323,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik raat merey paas se tashrif ley gaey aap ke tashrif ley janey par mein jazbaati hui, chunanche aap thodi der baad tashrif laye aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne meri haalat dekhi to farmaya : ''Aaisha ! kya hua, kya tum jazbaati ho gaee ho?'' maine arz kiya : mujhey kya hai ke mujh jaisi ko aap jaisey ki adam (ghair) mojudgi jazbaati na karey? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumharey paas tumhara shetan aaya hai.'' unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya merey sath shetan hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan !''maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya aap ke sath bhi hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan , lekin Allah ne uskey khilaf meri madad farmaee yahan tak ke main us se mehfooz rehta hun.'' rawahu Muslim."
3324,"Hazrat Abu-Salma , Fatima binte-Qais se riwayat kartey hain ke Abu-Amr bin Hafs ne unhen aakhiri Talaq us waqt di jab wo Madina Munawra se bahar they, chunanche Abu-Amr bin Hafs ke wakeel ne wo ''jo'' Fatima ke supurd kar diye jo Abu-Amr ne unke liye bhejey they wo us se naraz ho gaeen , is par (uskey wakeel) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! tumhara ham par koi haq nahin, chunanche wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur aap se uska tazkira kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumharey liye koi nafqa (bharan-poshan) nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen Umme-shareek ke ghar iddat guzarney ka hukm farmaya, phir farmaya : ''wo aisi khatoon hain ke merey Sahaba uskey paas aatey jatey hain, lihaza tum ibe Umme-Maktum (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan iddat guzaaro, kyonkey wo na-bina shakhs hai, tum apney mamool ke kapdey pehan kar reh sakti ho, jab tum iddat guzar lo to mujhey itilla karna.'' Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) kehti hain : jab maine iddat guzar li to maine aap ko bataya ke Muawiya bin Abi Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Jahm (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey peghame nikah bheja hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Jahm wo to apni lathi apney kandhey se nahin utaarta (sakht mizaj hai), aur raha Muawiya wo to faqir aadmi hai, uskey paas koi maal nahin, tum Usama bin Zaid se nikah kar lo.'' maine usey napasand kiya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Usama se nikah kar lo.'' maine us se nikah kar liya Allah ne is mein khair farma di, aur main qabile-rashk bin gaee . aur unhi se eik riwayat mein hai : ''Abu-Jahm ! wo to aurton ko bahut maarney wala hai.'' rawahu Muslim. aur eik riwayat mein hai ke uskey khawind ne jab usey teen talaaqein dey den to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aayen , to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''tumharey liye sirf hamila honey ki surat mein nafqa (bharan-poshan) hai, wesay koi nafqa nahin.''"
3325,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Fatima eik be abad ghar mein thin, unke mutalliq andesha mehsus kiya gaya isi liye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen rukhsat (choot) inayat farmaee, yani Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki murad ye hai ke isliye aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen (apney ghar sey) muntaqil honey ki ijazat di. aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ko kya ho gaya wo Allah se kyon nahin darti , jab wo ye kehti hai ke mutallaqa salaasa (teen Talaq paai hui) ke liye, ghar hai aur na kharcha. Bukhari."
3326,"Hazrat Saeed bin musaiyeb bayan kartey hain, Fatima (binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu)) ko mehaz isliye muntaqil kiya gaya ke wo apney (khaawind ke) aqaarib par zaban darazi karti thin. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
3327,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, meri khaala ko teen talaaqein di gaeen, unhoney apni khajuren todney ka irada kiya to eik aadmi ne unhen ghar se nikalney se mana kiya to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur waqia bayan kiya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kyon nahin, tum apni khajuren todo, kyonkey ummid hai ke tum sadqa karogi ya koi bhalai, neki ka kaam karogi.'' rawahu Muslim."
3328,"Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Sabeeaa Aslamiya ne apney khawind ki wafat ke chand din baad bachchey ko janm diya, phir wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin taake aap se nikah karney ki ijazat talab karen, aapney unhen ijazat ata farma di aur unhoney nikah kar liya. Bukhari."
3329,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, eik aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui to usney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! meri beti ka khawind faut ho gaya hai, aur uski aankh mein takleef hai, kya main uski aankh mein surma laga dun? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin.'' do baar ya teen baar, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) her baar yehi farmatey : ''nahin.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo (iddat) chaar maah das din hai, jabkey daure jahiliyat main tum mein se her koi saal ke ikhtitaam par oont ki mengni phainkti thi.'' (eik saal baad iddat khatam hoti thi) muttafaq aleh."
3330,"Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) aur Zenab bin Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah aur yoame-aakhirat par eman rakhney wali aurat ke liye halal nahin ke wo khawind ki wafat par chaar maah das din ke sog ke ilawa kisi aur maiyat par teen din se zayed sog karey.'' muttafaq aleh."
3331,"Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi aurat kisi maiyat par teen din se zayed sog na karey, albatta khawind par chaar maah das din ka sog karey, aur wo yamni lakeer daar chadar ke siwa rangey huey kapdey bhi na pehney , na surma daley aur na khushbu lagaey , albatta jab wo haiz se paak ho jaey to phir qust ya azfaar ki maamuli si khushbu laga ley.'' Bukhari, Muslim. aur Abu-Dawood ne ye izafa naqal kiya hai : ''wo mahndi na lagaey.'' muttafaq aleh, rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3332,"Hazrat Zenab binte Kab se riwayat hai ke Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan Furaiyya binte Maalik bin Sanan ne unhen bataya ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin taake wo apney qabiley bano khadra mein apney ghar chali jaey, kyonkey uska shohar apney mafrur ghulamon ki talash mein nikla tha jisey un ghulamon ne qatl kar diya tha, wo bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha ke main apney ghar walon ke paas chali jaaun kyonkey merey shohar ne na to apna zaati ghar chhoda hai aur na nafqa (bharan-poshan). wo bayan karti hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan.'' main wapis mudi yahan tak ke jab hujrey mein thi ya masjid mein thi to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey bulaaya aur farmaya : ''apney ghar mein raho yahan tak ke iddat puri ho jaey.'' wo bayan karti hain, maine wahan chaar maah das din iddat guzari. rawahu Malik, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, Nasai, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
3333,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) faut huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye to maine eilwey ka arq lagaya hua tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Umme-Salma ! ye kya hai? ''maine arz kiya : ye to eilwey ka arq hai ! is mein koi khushbu nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye chehrey ko chamka deta hai, isey raat ke waqt laga liya karo aur din ke waqt saaf kar diya karo, khushbu laga kar kanghi bhi na karo aur na mahndi laga kar kanghi karo, kyonkey wo khizaab hai.'' maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! main kis chiz ke sath kanghi karun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''beri (ke patton) ke sath, tum apney sar par unki lep kar liya karo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3334,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis aurat ka khawind faut ho jaey to wo na to zard rang ke kapdey pehney aur na surkh rang ke , aur na wo zewar pehney aur khizaab lagaey aur na hi surma lagaey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3335,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yasar se riwayat hai ke Ahwas ne Sham mein us waqt wafat pai jab uski biwi ko (Talaq ke baad) teesra haiz shuru ho chuka tha, wo usey Talaq dey chuka tha, Muawiya bin Abi Sufiyan ne is barey mein masla daryaft karney ke liye Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ke naam khat likha to Zaid ne unhen jawab diya ke wo teesrey haiz mein dakhil ho chuki hai, wo (aurat) us se bari hai aur wo us se bari hai, wo uska waris nahin aur ye uski waris nahin. rawahu Maalik."
3336,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyeb bayan kartey hain, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : jis aurat ko Talaq di gaee aur usey eik ya do haiz aagey aur phir uska haiz moquf ho gaya to wo nau-maah intizar karegi, agar uska hamal zahir ho gaya to phir yehi (waza' hai warna wo nau-maah ke baad teen maah iddat guzaareygi aur phir halal ho jaeygi. (aur wo dusri jagah nikah kar sakey gi) rawahu Maalik."
3337,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , eik aisi aurat ke paas se guzrey jo bachcha janne ke qarib thi to aapney uskey mutalliq sawal kiya to unhoney bataya ke ye falan shakhs ki londi hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya wo us se jima (sambhog) karta hai? '' unhoney arz kiya : ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine irada kiya ke main is par aisi lanat karun jo qabr tak uskey sath jaey, wo us se kaisey khidmat ka taqaza kar sakta hai jabkey wo uskey liye halal nahin, ya wo usey kaisey waris bana sakta hai jabkey wo uskey liye halal nahin.'' rawahu Muslim."
3338,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney ghazwae-autaas mein hasil honey wali laundiyon ke barey mein farmaya : ''waza' hamal se pehley hamila (londi) se jima (sambhog) na kiya jaey aur jo hamila nahin us se bhi jima na kiya jaey yahan tak ke usey eik haiz aa jaey.'' rawahu Ahmed, Abu-Dawood aur Darmi."
3339,"Hazrat Ruwefe bin Sabit Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hunain ke roz farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah aur yoame-aakhirat par eman rakhta ho, uskey liye halal nahin ke wo apna pani kisi aur ki kheti ko dey , yani hamila se jima (sambhog) karey, jo shakhs Allah aur roze-aakhirat par eman rakhta hai uskey liye halal nahin ke wo kisi londi se jima karey yahan tak ke uska rehem khaali ho jaey, aur jo shakhs Allah aur roze-aakhirat par eman rakhta hai uskey liye halal nahin ke wo maale-ghanimat ko uski taqseem se pehley farokht karey.'' Abu-Dawood. aur Imam Tirmizi ne usey (زَرْعَ غَیْرِہ) tak riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi."
3340,"Hazrat Imam Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, mujhey ye khabar pahunchi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un laundiyon ko jinhen haiz aata tha eik haiz ke zariey aur jinhen haiz nahin aata tha teen maah ke zariey istibraaey rehem ka hukm farmaya kartey they aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi ghair ki kheti ko pani deney se mana farmaya kartey they."
3341,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab aisi londi , jis se jima (sambhog) kiya jata ho, hiba ki jaey ya bai ki jaey ya azad ki jaey, to wo eik haiz ke zariey apney rehem ke khaali honey ka yaqin kar ley, aur kanwari se istibraaey rehem ka nahin kaha jaeyga.'' dono riwaayatein Rizeen ne riwayat ki hain. Rizeen."
3342,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Hind bante Utba ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! Abu-Sufiyaan eik bakheel aadmi hai, wo mujhey is qadr nahin deta jo merey aur meri aulad ke liye kafi ho, magar main us se is tarah ley leti hun ke usey pata nahin hota, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is qadr ley liya karo jo dastoor ke mutabiq terey aur teri aulad ke liye kafi ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
3343,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah tum mein se kisi ko maal ata karey to usey chahiye ke wo pehley apni zaat aur apney ghar walon par kharch karey.'' rawahu Muslim."
3344,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mamlook ka khana aur libas (dastoor ke mutabiq maalik par wajib) hai aur us se kaam sirf uski taqat ke mutabiq hi liya jaey.'' rawahu Muslim."
3345,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(ghulam) tumharey bhai hain, Allah ne unhen tumharey matehat kar diya hai, Allah jiskey bhai ko uskey matehat kar dey to wo usey wesa hi khilaaey jaisa khud khaye aur wesa hi pahnaaey jaisa khud pehney aur us se koi aisa kaam na ley jo uski taqat se ziyada ho, aur agar wo uskey zimmey koi aisa kaam laga dey jo uski taqat se badh kar ho to phir wo is mein uski madad karey.'' muttafaq aleh."
3346,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke unka munshi unke paas aaya to unhoney usey farmaya : kya tum ne ghulamon ko unke khaney ka saman dey diya hai? usney kaha : nahin, unhoney farmaya : jaao aur unhen (khaney ka saman) do, kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bandey ke liye yehi gunah kafi hai ke wo apney mamlook ke khaney ka saman rok ley.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''aadmi ke liye yehi gunah kafi hai ke jin ki khurak uskey zimmey hai wo uski rozi zaya kar dey.'' rawahu Muslim."
3347,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tumhara khaadim tumharey liye khana tayyar karkey laye to wo (malik) usey apney sath bithaaey taake wo khaye, kyonkey usney aag ki haraarat aur dhuwan bardasht kiya hai, agar khana , khaney walon ke hisab se kam ho to wo us main eik ya do luqmey uskey haath par rakh dey.'' rawahu Muslim."
3348,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab ghulam apney aaqa ke liye mukhlis aur khair chahey ho aur wo Allah ki ibadat bhi achchhe andaz mein karta ho to uskey liye do ajr hain.'' muttafaq aleh.
3349,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mamlook ke liye kya khub hai ke Allah usey us haal mein faut karey ke wo apney rab ki ibadat bhi achchhey andaz mein karta ho aur apney aaqa ki itaat bhi achchhey andaz mein karta ho, kya khub hai uskey liye.'' muttafaq aleh."
3350,"Hazrat Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab ghulam farar ho jata hai to uski Namaz qubul nahin ki jati.'' aur unhi se eik riwayat mein hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo ghulam farar ho jata hai to us se zimma khatam ho jata hai.'' aur unhi se eik aur riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo ghulam apney malikon se farar ho jaey to usney kufr kiya yahan tak ke wo unke paas laut aaye.'' rawahu Muslim."
3351,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jisney apney mamlook par bohtan baandha jabkey wo us se bari hai jo usney kaha to roze-qiyamat usey kodey maaren jaeyngey magar ye ke wo wesay hi ho jaisey usney kaha.'' muttafaq aleh."
3352,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jis shakhs ne apney ghulam par uskey nakarda jurm par had qaaim ki ya usko thappad raseed kiya to uska kaffara ye hai ke wo usey azad kar dey.'' rawahu Muslim."
3353,"Hazrat Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main apney ghulam ko maar raha tha usi doran maine apney peechey se eik aawaz suni : ''Abu-Masood ! jaan lo , Allah tum par is se kahin ziyada qudrat rakhta hai jitni tum is par qudrat rakhtey ho.'' maine peechey mud kar dekha to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) they, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! wo Allah ki raza ki khatir azad hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sun lo ! agar tum aisa na kartey to tumhen jahannam ki aag jalaat '' ya (farmaya) : ''tumhen aag chhooti.'' rawahu Muslim."
3354,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney arz kiya : merey paas maal hai, aur merey walid ko merey maal ki zarurat hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum aur tumhara maal terey walid ka hai, kyonkey tumhari aulad tumhari behtareen kamai hai, tum apni aulad ki kamai khaao.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3355,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney arz kiya : main faqir aadmi hun, merey paas kuchh bhi nahin, aur meri zere-nigrani eik yateem hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yateem ke maal se is tarah khaao ke is mein israaf (fizul kharchi) na ho, na jald bazi ho (ke yateem ke bada honey se pehley wo maal khatam ho jaey) aur na us se jaaidaad Banani chahiye.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood, Nasai aur ibne-Maja."
3356,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni maut ke marz mein farma rahey they : '' Namaz aur apney ghulamon ka khayal rakhna .'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi Shobil-eman ( ."
3357,Hazrat Imam Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se isi tarah riwayat kya hai. rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood .
3358,"Hazrat abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ghulamon ke sath bura sulook karney wala jannat mein dakhil nahin hoga .'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
3359,"Hazrat Raafe bin Makees (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ( ghulamon , riaaya sey) achcha sulook karney wala baaise-barkat hai jabkey burey akhlaq wala baaise-nahusat hai.'' aur main (sahibe-mishkat) ne masaabeh ke ilawa kisi aur nuskhey mein ye izafa nahin dekha jo sahibe-masaabeh ne naqal kya hai : ''sadqa buri maut se bachata hai aur neki umr mein izafa ka baais hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3360,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi apney khaadim ko maarey aur wo Allah ka wasta dey to tum apna haath utha lo (na maaro) .'' Tirmizi, Behaqi fi Shobil-eman , lekin is mein '' apna haath utha lo '' ke bajaey '' rok lo '' ke alfaz hain. ( rawahu Tirmizi w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
3361,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' jisney walida aur uskey bachey ke darmiyan judai dal di to roze-qiyamat Allah uskey aur uskey chaheeton ( waliden aur aulad waghera) ke darmiyan judai dal dega .'' rawahu Tirmizi w Darmi ."
3362,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do ghulam bhai mujhey hiba kiye to maine un mein se eik bech diya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se daryaft farmaya : ''tera ghulam kahan gaya?'' maine aap ko bataya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey wapis laao, usey wapis laao.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
3363,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney eik londi aur uskey bachey ke darmiyan judai dal di to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen us se mana farmaya aur saude ko khatm kar diya. Abu-Dawood ne usey munqata riwayat kya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood .
3364,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs mein teen sifaat hongi Allah uski maut aasan farma dega aur usey jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga : kamzor se narmi karna , waliden par shafqat karna aur mamlook se ehsan karna.'' Tirmizi . aur unhoney kaha : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
3365,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko eik ghulam hiba kya to farmaya : ''usey maarna nahin, kyonkey namaaziyon ko maarney se mana kya gaya hai aur maine usey Namaz padhtey huey dekha hai.'' ye masaabeh ke alfaz hain. ( rawahu al-baghwi fi المصابیح w Ahmed w Tabrani ( ."
3366,aur Imam daarqutni ki riwayat al-mujtaba mein hai ke umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen namaaziyon ko maarney se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Dar-Qutni .
3367,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! ham khaadim ko kitni baar maaf keren? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khamosh rahey, us shakhs ne phir yehi kaha, aap phir khamosh rahey, jab teesri baar puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us se din mein sattar baar darguzar karo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3368,Hazrat Imam Tirmizi ne usey Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu Tirmizi .
3369,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumharey ghulamon mein se jo ghulam tumhari madad karey to jo tum khatey ho usey bhi wohi khilao aur jo tum pehantey ho usey bhi wohi pehnao, aur un mein se jo tumhari muaawinat na karey usey bech do aur Allah ki makhluq ko saza na do.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood ."
3370,"Hazrat Sehal bin Hanzala (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik laaghar oont ke paas se guzrey to farmaya : '' un be zaban janweron ke barey mein Allah se daro, un par us haal mein sawari karo ke wo sawari ke qabil hon, aur unhen is haal mein chhodo ke wo achey hun ( abhi thakey na hun) .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3371,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Allah Taala ka farman : ''tum yateem ke maal ke qarib na jaao magar usi ke sath ke wo ahsan ho.'' uska farman : '' be-shak jo log yateemon ka maal zulm karkey khatey hain.'' nazil hua to phir jis shakhs ke paas yateem tha usney uska khana apney khaney sey, uska peena apney peeney se alag kar diya, aur jab yateem ke khaney peeney se kuch bach jata to wo usi ke liye rakh detey yahan tak ke wo usey kha leta ya wo kharab ho jata, ye chiz un par bahut dushwaar guzri to unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska tazkira kya is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaai : '' wo aap se yateemon ke barey mein daryaft kartey hain, farma dijiye unke liye islah karna behtar hai, aur agar tum unko apney sath mila lo to wo tumharey bhai hain.'' unhoney unka khana apney khaney ke sath aur peena apney peeney ke sath mila liya . rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
3372,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne walid aur uskey bachey ke darmiyan, neez bhaiyon ke darmiyan judai dalney waley par lanat farmaai. rawahu ibne-Maja w Dar-Qutni ."
3373,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas qaidi laye jatey to aap eik ghar ke tamam afrad kisi eik ko ata farma detey kyonkey aapko un mein judai dalna napasand tha. rawahu ibne-Maja."
3374,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen tumharey burey logon ke mutalliq na bataaun, wo shakhs hai jo (bukhl w takabbur ki wajeh sey) akela khata hai, apney ghulam ko maarta hai aur apna Atiya uskey mustahiq ko nahin deta.'' rawahu rizeen."
3375,"Hazrat abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(mamlookon sey) bura sulook karney wala jannat mein nahin jaeyga.'' Sahaba kiram ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya aapney hamen nahin bataya ke is ummat mein tamam ummaton se ziyada mamlook aur yateem hongey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan, tum unki apni aulad ki tarah takrim karo aur jo khud khaao wohi unhen khilao.'' unhoney arz kya : hamen duniya mein kon si chiz faeyda degi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ghoda jisey to tayyar rakhey taake to is par Allah ki raah mein jihad karey, aur mamlook jo tujhey kifaayat karey, jab wo Namaz padhey to wo tumhara bhai hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ."
3376,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ghazwae uhad ke moqe par chaudah saal ki umr mein mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiya gaya to aapney mujhey wapis kar diya, phir ghazwae khandaq ke moqe par pandarah saal ki umr mein mujhey pesh kiya gaya to aapney mujhey (jihad karney ki) ijazat marahmat farma di. umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : yehi umr (pandarah saal) ladney waley jawaanon aur ladkon (naabaaligh) mein farq karney wali hai. muttafaq aleh."
3377,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hudebiya ke moqe par teen ashiya (chizon) par suleh farmaee, ke mushrekin mein se jo shakhs unki taraf aaeyga usey un (mushrekin) ki taraf wapis kiya jaeyga. aur jo musalmanon ki taraf se unke paas chala jaey to usey wapis nahin kiya jaeyga, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aainda saal Makka mein dakhil hongey. aur wahan teen roz qiyam karengey, jab aap is (Makka) mein dakhil huey aur muddat puri ho gaee aur aapney wapsi ka irada farmaya to Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey chacha jaan ! chacha jaan ! keh kar aawazen deney lagi to Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne uska haath pakad kar apney sath kar liya uskey sath hi Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) , Hazrat Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) , aur Hazrat Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ke darmiyan Hamza ki beti ke barey mein tanaaza' shuru ho gaya : Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maine usey pakda hai aur wo merey chacha ki beti hai, Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : wo merey chacha ki beti hai aur uski khaala meri biwi hai, aur Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : merey bhai ki beti hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq uski khaala ke haq mein faisla kiya aur farmaya : ''khaala maa ki jagah par hai.'' aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''tum mujh se ho aur main tujh se hun.'' Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''tum (خَلق w خُلق ( (seerat aur soorat) mein mujh se mushabeh ho.'' aur Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''tum hamarey bhai aur hamarey chahetey ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
3378,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke eik aurat ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! mera ye beta (ke dorane hamal) mera pet uskey liye bartan tha, (doodh pilate waqt) meri chhaati uskey liye mishkeeza (doodh peeney ki jagah)  thi. aur meri god uskey liye thikana thi, aur (ab) uskey walid ne mujhey Talaq de-di hai aur wo usey mujh se chheennaa chahta hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tak tu  (naey khawind sey) nikah na karey, us waqt tak tum uski ziyada haq daar ho.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
3379,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne baligh ladkey ko uskey walid aur uski walida ke darmiyan ikhtiyar diya. rawahu Tirmizi.
3380,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui to usney arz kiya, mera khawind merey is bete ko ley jana chahta hai, jabkey wo merey liye pani lata hai aur mujhey faeyda pahunchata hai, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye tumhara walid hai aur ye tumhari walida hai, tum un dono mein se jis ka chaho haath thaam lo.'' usney apni walida ka haath thaam liya to wo usey lekar chali gaee. rawahu Abu-Dawood, Nasai aur Darmi."
3381,"Hazrat Hilal bin Usama ehle Madina ke azad karda ghulam Abu Maimuna Suleman (Alaihissalam) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha is doran ke main Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas betha hua tha ke eik Farsi (ajmi) aurat, jis ko uskey khawind (shohar) ne Talaq de-di thi, apney bete ko lekar Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aai aur wo dono (walid aur walida) uska daawa kartey they, us aurat ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se Farsi mein baat kartey huey kaha : Abu-Hurera ! mera khawind merey is bete ko ley jana chahta hai. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : tum dono iskey mutalliq qura andazi karo. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi uskey mutalliq usey Farsi mein bataya , jab uska khawind aaya to usney kaha : merey bete ke mutalliq kon mujh se jhagadta hai? Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : aey Allah ! main ye faisla isliye dey raha hun ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas betha hua tha ke eik aurat aap ki khidmat mein hazir hui to usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! mera khawind merey is bete ko ley jana chahta hai, jabkey wo mujhey faeyda pahunchata hai aur Abu Anba ke kunwen se pani la kar mujhey pilata hai, aur Nasai ki riwayat mein hai : mitha pani. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''iskey mutalliq qura andazi karo.'' to uskey khawind ne kaha : merey bachey ke barey mein mujh se kon jhagadta hai? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye tera walid hai aur ye teri walida hai, lihaza tum un mein se jis ka chaho haath pakad lo.'' usney apni walida ka haath pakad liya. Abu-Dawud, Nasai , lekin unhoney usey musnad riwayat kiya hai. aur Darmi ne usey Hilal bin Usama se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood, Nasai aur Darmi."
